var book = {
	"name": "Job",
	"numChapters": 42,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the land of Uz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871A\"></sup> there lived a man whose name was Job.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871B\"></sup> This man was blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871C\"></sup> and upright;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871D\"></sup> he feared God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871E\"></sup> and shunned evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12871F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12871F\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He had seven sons<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12872G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12872G\"></sup> and three daughters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12872H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12872H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and he owned seven thousand sheep, three thousand camels, five hundred yoke of oxen and five hundred donkeys,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12873I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12873I\"></sup> and had a large number of servants.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12873J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12873J\"></sup> He was the greatest man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12873K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12873K\"></sup> among all the people of the East.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12873L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12873L\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His sons used to hold feasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12874M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12874M\"></sup> in their homes on their birthdays, and they would invite their three sisters to eat and drink with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When a period of feasting had run its course, Job would make arrangements for them to be purified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12875N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12875N\"></sup> Early in the morning he would sacrifice a burnt offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12875O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12875O\"></sup> for each of them, thinking, “Perhaps my children have sinned<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12875P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12875P\"></sup> and cursed God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12875Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12875Q\"></sup> in their hearts.” This was Job’s regular custom.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>One day the angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12876R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12876R\"></sup> came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12876S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12876S\"></sup> also came with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12876T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12876T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Where have you come from?”Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “From roaming throughout the earth, going back and forth on it.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12877U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12877U\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you considered my servant Job?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12878V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12878V\"></sup> There is no one on earth like him; he is blameless and upright, a man who fears God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12878W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12878W\"></sup> and shuns evil.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12878X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12878X\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Does Job fear God for nothing?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12879Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12879Y\"></sup> Satan replied.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Have you not put a hedge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12880Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12880Z\"></sup> around him and his household and everything he has?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12880AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12880AA\"></sup> You have blessed the work of his hands, so that his flocks and herds are spread throughout the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12880AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12880AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now stretch out your hand and strike everything he has,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12881AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12881AC\"></sup> and he will surely curse you to your face.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12881AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12881AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Very well, then, everything he has<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12882AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12882AE\"></sup> is in your power, but on the man himself do not lay a finger.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12882AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12882AF\"></sup>Then Satan went out from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>One day when Job’s sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12883AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12883AG\"></sup> were feasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12883AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12883AH\"></sup> and drinking wine at the oldest brother’s house,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>a messenger came to Job and said, “The oxen were plowing and the donkeys were grazing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12884AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12884AI\"></sup> nearby,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and the Sabeans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12885AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12885AJ\"></sup> attacked and made off with them. They put the servants to the sword, and I am the only one who has escaped to tell you!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>While he was still speaking, another messenger came and said, “The fire of God fell from the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12886AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12886AK\"></sup> and burned up the sheep and the servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12886AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12886AL\"></sup> and I am the only one who has escaped to tell you!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>While he was still speaking, another messenger came and said, “The Chaldeans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12887AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12887AM\"></sup> formed three raiding parties and swept down on your camels and made off with them. They put the servants to the sword, and I am the only one who has escaped to tell you!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>While he was still speaking, yet another messenger came and said, “Your sons and daughters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12888AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12888AN\"></sup> were feasting<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12888AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12888AO\"></sup> and drinking wine at the oldest brother’s house,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>when suddenly a mighty wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12889AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12889AP\"></sup> swept in from the desert and struck the four corners of the house. It collapsed on them and they are dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12889AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12889AQ\"></sup> and I am the only one who has escaped to tell you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12889AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12889AR\"></sup>”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>At this, Job got up and tore his robe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12890AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12890AS\"></sup> and shaved his head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12890AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12890AT\"></sup> Then he fell to the ground in worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12890AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12890AU\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and said:“Naked I came from my mother’s womb,and naked I will depart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12891AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12891AV\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has taken away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12891AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12891AW\"></sup>may the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be praised.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12891AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12891AX\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In all this, Job did not sin by charging God with wrongdoing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12892AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12892AY\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>On another day the angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12893A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12893A\"></sup> came to present themselves before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and Satan also came with them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12893B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12893B\"></sup> to present himself before him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Where have you come from?”Satan answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “From roaming throughout the earth, going back and forth on it.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12894C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12894C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Have you considered my servant Job? There is no one on earth like him; he is blameless and upright, a man who fears God and shuns evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12895D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12895D\"></sup> And he still maintains his integrity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12895E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12895E\"></sup> though you incited me against him to ruin him without any reason.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12895F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12895F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Skin for skin!” Satan replied. “A man will give all he has<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12896G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12896G\"></sup> for his own life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But now stretch out your hand and strike his flesh and bones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12897H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12897H\"></sup> and he will surely curse you to your face.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12897I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12897I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Satan, “Very well, then, he is in your hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12898J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12898J\"></sup> but you must spare his life.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12898K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12898K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So Satan went out from the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and afflicted Job with painful sores from the soles of his feet to the crown of his head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12899L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12899L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Job took a piece of broken pottery and scraped himself with it as he sat among the ashes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12900M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12900M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>His wife said to him, “Are you still maintaining your integrity?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12901N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12901N\"></sup> Curse God and die!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12901O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12901O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He replied, “You are talking like a foolish woman. Shall we accept good from God, and not trouble?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12902P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12902P\"></sup>In all this, Job did not sin in what he said.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12902Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12902Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Job’s three friends, Eliphaz the Temanite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12903R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12903R\"></sup> Bildad the Shuhite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12903S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12903S\"></sup> and Zophar the Naamathite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12903T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12903T\"></sup> heard about all the troubles that had come upon him, they set out from their homes and met together by agreement to go and sympathize with him and comfort him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12903U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12903U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they saw him from a distance, they could hardly recognize him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12904V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12904V\"></sup> they began to weep aloud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12904W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12904W\"></sup> and they tore their robes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12904X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12904X\"></sup> and sprinkled dust on their heads.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12904Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12904Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then they sat on the ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12905Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12905Z\"></sup> with him for seven days and seven nights.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12905AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12905AA\"></sup> No one said a word to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12905AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12905AB\"></sup> because they saw how great his suffering was."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>After this, Job opened his mouth and cursed the day of his birth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12906A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12906A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He said:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“May the day of my birth perish,and the night that said, ‘A boy is conceived!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12908B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12908B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>That day—may it turn to darkness;may God above not care about it;may no light shine on it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>May gloom and utter darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12910C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12910C\"></sup> claim it once more;may a cloud settle over it;may blackness overwhelm it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>That night—may thick darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12911D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12911D\"></sup> seize it;may it not be included among the days of the yearnor be entered in any of the months.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>May that night be barren;may no shout of joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12912E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12912E\"></sup> be heard in it.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>May those who curse days curse that day,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12913F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12913F\"></sup>those who are ready to rouse Leviathan.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12913G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12913G\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>May its morning stars become dark;may it wait for daylight in vainand not see the first rays of dawn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12914H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12914H\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>for it did not shut the doors of the womb on meto hide trouble from my eyes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Why did I not perish at birth,and die as I came from the womb?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12916I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12916I\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Why were there knees to receive me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12917J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12917J\"></sup>and breasts that I might be nursed?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For now I would be lying down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12918K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12918K\"></sup> in peace;I would be asleep and at rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12918L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12918L\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>with kings and rulers of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12919M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12919M\"></sup>who built for themselves places now lying in ruins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12919N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12919N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>with princes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12920O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12920O\"></sup> who had gold,who filled their houses with silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12920P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12920P\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Or why was I not hidden away in the ground like a stillborn child,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12921Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12921Q\"></sup>like an infant who never saw the light of day?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12921R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12921R\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>There the wicked cease from turmoil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12922S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12922S\"></sup>and there the weary are at rest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12922T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12922T\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Captives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12923U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12923U\"></sup> also enjoy their ease;they no longer hear the slave driver’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12923V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12923V\"></sup> shout.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12923W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12923W\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The small and the great are there,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12924X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12924X\"></sup>and the slaves are freed from their owners.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Why is light given to those in misery,and life to the bitter of soul,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12925Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12925Y\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>to those who long for death that does not come,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12926Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12926Z\"></sup>who search for it more than for hidden treasure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12926AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12926AA\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>who are filled with gladnessand rejoice when they reach the grave?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12927AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12927AB\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Why is life given to a manwhose way is hidden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12928AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12928AC\"></sup>whom God has hedged in?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12928AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12928AD\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For sighing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12929AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12929AE\"></sup> has become my daily food;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12929AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12929AF\"></sup>my groans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12929AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12929AG\"></sup> pour out like water.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12929AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12929AH\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>What I feared has come upon me;what I dreaded<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12930AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12930AI\"></sup> has happened to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12930AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12930AJ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I have no peace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12931AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12931AK\"></sup> no quietness;I have no rest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12931AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12931AL\"></sup> but only turmoil.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12931AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12931AM\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12932A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12932A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“If someone ventures a word with you, will you be impatient?But who can keep from speaking?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12933B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12933B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Think how you have instructed many,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12934C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12934C\"></sup>how you have strengthened feeble hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12934D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12934D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your words have supported those who stumbled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12935E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12935E\"></sup>you have strengthened faltering knees.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12935F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12935F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But now trouble comes to you, and you are discouraged;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12936G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12936G\"></sup>it strikes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12936H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12936H\"></sup> you, and you are dismayed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12936I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12936I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Should not your piety be your confidence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12937J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12937J\"></sup>and your blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12937K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12937K\"></sup> ways your hope?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Consider now: Who, being innocent, has ever perished?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12938L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12938L\"></sup>Where were the upright ever destroyed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12938M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12938M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>As I have observed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12939N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12939N\"></sup> those who plow evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12939O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12939O\"></sup>and those who sow trouble reap it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12939P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12939P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>At the breath of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12940Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12940Q\"></sup> they perish;at the blast of his anger they are no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12940R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12940R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The lions may roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12941S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12941S\"></sup> and growl,yet the teeth of the great lions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12941T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12941T\"></sup> are broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12941U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12941U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The lion perishes for lack of prey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12942V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12942V\"></sup>and the cubs of the lioness are scattered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12942W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12942W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“A word<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12943X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12943X\"></sup> was secretly brought to me,my ears caught a whisper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12943Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12943Y\"></sup> of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12943Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12943Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Amid disquieting dreams in the night,when deep sleep falls on people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12944AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12944AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>fear and trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12945AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12945AB\"></sup> seized meand made all my bones shake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12945AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12945AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>A spirit glided past my face,and the hair on my body stood on end.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12946AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12946AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It stopped,but I could not tell what it was.A form stood before my eyes,and I heard a hushed voice:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12947AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12947AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Can a mortal be more righteous than God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12948AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12948AF\"></sup>Can even a strong man be more pure than his Maker?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12948AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12948AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>If God places no trust in his servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12949AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12949AH\"></sup>if he charges his angels with error,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12949AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12949AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>how much more those who live in houses of clay,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12950AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12950AJ\"></sup>whose foundations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12950AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12950AK\"></sup> are in the dust,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12950AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12950AL\"></sup>who are crushed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12950AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12950AM\"></sup> more readily than a moth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12950AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12950AN\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Between dawn and dusk they are broken to pieces;unnoticed, they perish forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12951AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12951AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Are not the cords of their tent pulled up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12952AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12952AP\"></sup>so that they die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12952AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12952AQ\"></sup> without wisdom?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12952AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12952AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Call if you will, but who will answer you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12953A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12953A\"></sup>To which of the holy ones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12953B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12953B\"></sup> will you turn?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Resentment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12954C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12954C\"></sup> kills a fool,and envy slays the simple.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12954D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12954D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I myself have seen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12955E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12955E\"></sup> a fool taking root,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12955F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12955F\"></sup>but suddenly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12955G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12955G\"></sup> his house was cursed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12955H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12955H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12956I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12956I\"></sup> are far from safety,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12956J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12956J\"></sup>crushed in court<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12956K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12956K\"></sup> without a defender.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12956L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12956L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The hungry consume his harvest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12957M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12957M\"></sup>taking it even from among thorns,and the thirsty pant after his wealth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For hardship does not spring from the soil,nor does trouble sprout from the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12958N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12958N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet man is born to trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12959O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12959O\"></sup>as surely as sparks fly upward.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But if I were you, I would appeal to God;I would lay my cause before him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12960P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12960P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He performs wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12961Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12961Q\"></sup> that cannot be fathomed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12961R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12961R\"></sup>miracles that cannot be counted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12961S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12961S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He provides rain for the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12962T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12962T\"></sup>he sends water on the countryside.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12962U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12962U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The lowly he sets on high,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12963V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12963V\"></sup>and those who mourn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12963W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12963W\"></sup> are lifted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12963X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12963X\"></sup> to safety.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He thwarts the plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12964Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12964Y\"></sup> of the crafty,so that their hands achieve no success.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12964Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12964Z\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He catches the wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12965AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12965AA\"></sup> in their craftiness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12965AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12965AB\"></sup>and the schemes of the wily are swept away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12965AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12965AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12966AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12966AD\"></sup> comes upon them in the daytime;at noon they grope as in the night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12966AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12966AE\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He saves the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12967AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12967AF\"></sup> from the sword in their mouth;he saves them from the clutches of the powerful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12967AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12967AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12968AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12968AH\"></sup> have hope,and injustice shuts its mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12968AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12968AI\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Blessed is the one whom God corrects;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12969AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12969AJ\"></sup>so do not despise the discipline<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12969AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12969AK\"></sup> of the Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12969AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12969AL\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For he wounds, but he also binds up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12970AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12970AM\"></sup>he injures, but his hands also heal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12970AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12970AN\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>From six calamities he will rescue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12971AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12971AO\"></sup> you;in seven no harm will touch you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12971AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12971AP\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In famine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12972AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12972AQ\"></sup> he will deliver you from death,and in battle from the stroke of the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12972AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12972AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You will be protected from the lash of the tongue,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12973AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12973AS\"></sup>and need not fear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12973AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12973AT\"></sup> when destruction comes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12973AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12973AU\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You will laugh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12974AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12974AV\"></sup> at destruction and famine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12974AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12974AW\"></sup>and need not fear the wild animals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12974AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12974AX\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For you will have a covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12975AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12975AY\"></sup> with the stones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12975AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12975AZ\"></sup> of the field,and the wild animals will be at peace with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12975BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12975BA\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You will know that your tent is secure;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12976BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12976BB\"></sup>you will take stock of your property and find nothing missing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12976BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12976BC\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>You will know that your children will be many,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12977BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12977BD\"></sup>and your descendants like the grass of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12977BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12977BE\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You will come to the grave in full vigor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12978BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12978BF\"></sup>like sheaves gathered in season.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12978BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12978BG\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“We have examined this, and it is true.So hear it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12979BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12979BH\"></sup> and apply it to yourself.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12979BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12979BI\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“If only my anguish could be weighedand all my misery be placed on the scales!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12981A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12981A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It would surely outweigh the sand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12982B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12982B\"></sup> of the seas—no wonder my words have been impetuous.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12982C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12982C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The arrows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983D\"></sup> of the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983E\"></sup> are in me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983F\"></sup>my spirit drinks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983G\"></sup> in their poison;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983H\"></sup>God’s terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983I\"></sup> are marshaled against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12983J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12983J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Does a wild donkey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12984K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12984K\"></sup> bray<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12984L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12984L\"></sup> when it has grass,or an ox bellow when it has fodder?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12984M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12984M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Is tasteless food eaten without salt,or is there flavor in the sap of the mallow?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12985N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12985N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I refuse to touch it;such food makes me ill.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12986O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12986O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Oh, that I might have my request,that God would grant what I hope for,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12987P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12987P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>that God would be willing to crush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12988Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12988Q\"></sup> me,to let loose his hand and cut off my life!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12988R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12988R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then I would still have this consolation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12989S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12989S\"></sup>—my joy in unrelenting pain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12989T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12989T\"></sup>—that I had not denied the words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12989U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12989U\"></sup> of the Holy One.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12989V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12989V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“What strength do I have, that I should still hope?What prospects, that I should be patient?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12990W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12990W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Do I have the strength of stone?Is my flesh bronze?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12991X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12991X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do I have any power to help myself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12992Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12992Y\"></sup>now that success has been driven from me?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Anyone who withholds kindness from a friend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12993Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12993Z\"></sup>forsakes the fear of the Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12993AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12993AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But my brothers are as undependable as intermittent streams,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12994AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12994AB\"></sup>as the streams that overflow",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>when darkened by thawing iceand swollen with melting snow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12995AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12995AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>but that stop flowing in the dry season,and in the heat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12996AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12996AD\"></sup> vanish from their channels.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Caravans turn aside from their routes;they go off into the wasteland and perish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The caravans of Tema<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12998AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12998AE\"></sup> look for water,the traveling merchants of Sheba<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12998AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12998AF\"></sup> look in hope.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They are distressed, because they had been confident;they arrive there, only to be disappointed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-12999AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-12999AG\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now you too have proved to be of no help;you see something dreadful and are afraid.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13000AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13000AH\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Have I ever said, ‘Give something on my behalf,pay a ransom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13001AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13001AI\"></sup> for me from your wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13001AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13001AJ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>deliver me from the hand of the enemy,rescue me from the clutches of the ruthless’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13002AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13002AK\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Teach me, and I will be quiet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13003AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13003AL\"></sup>show me where I have been wrong.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13003AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13003AM\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>How painful are honest words!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13004AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13004AN\"></sup>But what do your arguments prove?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Do you mean to correct what I say,and treat my desperate words as wind?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13005AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13005AO\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You would even cast lots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13006AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13006AP\"></sup> for the fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13006AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13006AQ\"></sup>and barter away your friend.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But now be so kind as to look at me.Would I lie to your face?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13007AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13007AR\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Relent, do not be unjust;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13008AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13008AS\"></sup>reconsider, for my integrity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13008AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13008AT\"></sup> is at stake.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13008AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13008AU\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Is there any wickedness on my lips?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13009AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13009AV\"></sup>Can my mouth not discern<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13009AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13009AW\"></sup> malice?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>“Do not mortals have hard service<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13010A\"></sup> on earth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13010B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13010B\"></sup>Are not their days like those of hired laborers?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13010C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13010C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like a slave longing for the evening shadows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13011D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13011D\"></sup>or a hired laborer waiting to be paid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13011E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13011E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>so I have been allotted months of futility,and nights of misery have been assigned to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13012F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13012F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When I lie down I think, ‘How long before I get up?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13013G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13013G\"></sup>The night drags on, and I toss and turn until dawn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13013H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13013H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My body is clothed with worms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13014I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13014I\"></sup> and scabs,my skin is broken and festering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13014J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13014J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“My days are swifter than a weaver’s shuttle,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13015K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13015K\"></sup>and they come to an end without hope.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13015L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13015L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Remember, O God, that my life is but a breath;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13016M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13016M\"></sup>my eyes will never see happiness again.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13016N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13016N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The eye that now sees me will see me no longer;you will look for me, but I will be no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13017O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13017O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As a cloud vanishes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13018P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13018P\"></sup> and is gone,so one who goes down to the grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13018Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13018Q\"></sup> does not return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13018R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13018R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He will never come to his house again;his place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13019S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13019S\"></sup> will know him no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13019T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13019T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Therefore I will not keep silent;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13020U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13020U\"></sup>I will speak out in the anguish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13020V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13020V\"></sup> of my spirit,I will complain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13020W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13020W\"></sup> in the bitterness of my soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13020X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13020X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Am I the sea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13021Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13021Y\"></sup> or the monster of the deep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13021Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13021Z\"></sup>that you put me under guard?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13021AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13021AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When I think my bed will comfort meand my couch will ease my complaint,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13022AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13022AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>even then you frighten me with dreamsand terrify<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13023AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13023AC\"></sup> me with visions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13023AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13023AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so that I prefer strangling and death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13024AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13024AE\"></sup>rather than this body of mine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13024AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13024AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I despise my life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13025AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13025AG\"></sup> I would not live forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13025AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13025AH\"></sup>Let me alone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13025AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13025AI\"></sup> my days have no meaning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13025AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13025AJ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“What is mankind that you make so much of them,that you give them so much attention,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13026AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13026AK\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>that you examine them every morning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13027AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13027AL\"></sup>and test them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13027AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13027AM\"></sup> every moment?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13027AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13027AN\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Will you never look away from me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13028AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13028AO\"></sup>or let me alone even for an instant?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13028AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13028AP\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>If I have sinned, what have I done to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13029AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13029AQ\"></sup>you who see everything we do?Why have you made me your target?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13029AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13029AR\"></sup>Have I become a burden to you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13029AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13029AS\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Why do you not pardon my offensesand forgive my sins?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13030AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13030AT\"></sup>For I will soon lie down in the dust;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13030AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13030AU\"></sup>you will search for me, but I will be no more.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13030AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13030AV\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13031A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13031A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you say such things?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13032B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13032B\"></sup>Your words are a blustering wind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13032C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Does God pervert justice?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13033D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13033D\"></sup>Does the Almighty pervert what is right?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13033E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13033E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When your children sinned against him,he gave them over to the penalty of their sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13034F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13034F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But if you will seek God earnestlyand plead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13035G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13035G\"></sup> with the Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13035H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13035H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>if you are pure and upright,even now he will rouse himself on your behalf<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13036I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13036I\"></sup>and restore you to your prosperous state.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13036J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13036J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your beginnings will seem humble,so prosperous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13037K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13037K\"></sup> will your future be.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13037L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13037L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Ask the former generation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13038M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13038M\"></sup>and find out what their ancestors learned,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for we were born only yesterday and know nothing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13039N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13039N\"></sup>and our days on earth are but a shadow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13039O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13039O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Will they not instruct<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13040P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13040P\"></sup> you and tell you?Will they not bring forth words from their understanding?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13040Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13040Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Can papyrus grow tall where there is no marsh?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13041R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13041R\"></sup>Can reeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13041S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13041S\"></sup> thrive without water?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While still growing and uncut,they wither more quickly than grass.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13042T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13042T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Such is the destiny<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13043U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13043U\"></sup> of all who forget God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13043V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13043V\"></sup>so perishes the hope of the godless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13043W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13043W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>What they trust in is fragile;what they rely on is a spider’s web.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13044X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13044X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They lean on the web,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13045Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13045Y\"></sup> but it gives way;they cling to it, but it does not hold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13045Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13045Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They are like a well-watered plant in the sunshine,spreading its shoots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13046AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13046AA\"></sup> over the garden;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13046AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13046AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>it entwines its roots around a pile of rocksand looks for a place among the stones.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But when it is torn from its spot,that place disowns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13048AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13048AC\"></sup> it and says, ‘I never saw you.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13048AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13048AD\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Surely its life withers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13049AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13049AE\"></sup> away,and from the soil other plants grow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13049AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13049AF\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Surely God does not reject one who is blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13050AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13050AG\"></sup>or strengthen the hands of evildoers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13050AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13050AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He will yet fill your mouth with laughter<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13051AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13051AI\"></sup>and your lips with shouts of joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13051AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13051AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your enemies will be clothed in shame,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13052AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13052AK\"></sup>and the tents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13052AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13052AL\"></sup> of the wicked will be no more.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13052AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13052AM\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Indeed, I know that this is true.But how can mere mortals prove their innocence before God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13054A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Though they wished to dispute with him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13055B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13055B\"></sup>they could not answer him one time out of a thousand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13055C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13055C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13056D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13056D\"></sup> is profound, his power is vast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13056E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13056E\"></sup>Who has resisted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13056F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13056F\"></sup> him and come out unscathed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13056G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13056G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He moves mountains<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13057H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13057H\"></sup> without their knowing itand overturns them in his anger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13057I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13057I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He shakes the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13058J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13058J\"></sup> from its placeand makes its pillars tremble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13058K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13058K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He speaks to the sun and it does not shine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13059L\"></sup>he seals off the light of the stars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13059M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13059M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He alone stretches out the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13060N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13060N\"></sup>and treads on the waves of the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13060O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13060O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He is the Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13061P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13061P\"></sup> of the Bear and Orion,the Pleiades and the constellations of the south.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13061Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13061Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He performs wonders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13062R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13062R\"></sup> that cannot be fathomed,miracles that cannot be counted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13062S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13062S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When he passes me, I cannot see him;when he goes by, I cannot perceive him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13063T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13063T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If he snatches away, who can stop him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13064U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13064U\"></sup>Who can say to him, ‘What are you doing?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13064V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13064V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>God does not restrain his anger;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13065W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13065W\"></sup>even the cohorts of Rahab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13065X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13065X\"></sup> cowered at his feet.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“How then can I dispute with him?How can I find words to argue with him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13066Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13066Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though I were innocent, I could not answer him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13067Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13067Z\"></sup>I could only plead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13067AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13067AA\"></sup> with my Judge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13067AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13067AB\"></sup> for mercy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13067AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13067AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Even if I summoned him and he responded,I do not believe he would give me a hearing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13068AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13068AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He would crush me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13069AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13069AE\"></sup> with a storm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13069AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13069AF\"></sup>and multiply<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13069AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13069AG\"></sup> my wounds for no reason.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13069AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13069AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He would not let me catch my breathbut would overwhelm me with misery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13070AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13070AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If it is a matter of strength, he is mighty!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13071AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13071AJ\"></sup>And if it is a matter of justice, who can challenge him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13071AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13071AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Even if I were innocent, my mouth would condemn me;if I were blameless, it would pronounce me guilty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13072AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13072AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Although I am blameless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13073AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13073AM\"></sup>I have no concern for myself;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13073AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13073AN\"></sup>I despise my own life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13073AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13073AO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It is all the same; that is why I say,‘He destroys both the blameless and the wicked.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13074AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13074AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When a scourge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13075AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13075AQ\"></sup> brings sudden death,he mocks the despair of the innocent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13075AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13075AR\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When a land falls into the hands of the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13076AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13076AS\"></sup>he blindfolds its judges.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13076AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13076AT\"></sup>If it is not he, then who is it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13076AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13076AU\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“My days are swifter than a runner;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13077AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13077AV\"></sup>they fly away without a glimpse of joy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13077AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13077AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They skim past<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13078AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13078AX\"></sup> like boats of papyrus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13078AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13078AY\"></sup>like eagles swooping down on their prey.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13078AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13078AZ\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If I say, ‘I will forget my complaint,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13079BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13079BA\"></sup>I will change my expression, and smile,’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I still dread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13080BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13080BB\"></sup> all my sufferings,for I know you will not hold me innocent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13080BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13080BC\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Since I am already found guilty,why should I struggle in vain?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13081BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13081BD\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Even if I washed myself with soap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13082BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13082BE\"></sup>and my hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13082BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13082BF\"></sup> with cleansing powder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13082BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13082BG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>you would plunge me into a slime pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13083BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13083BH\"></sup>so that even my clothes would detest me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13083BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13083BI\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“He is not a mere mortal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13084BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13084BJ\"></sup> like me that I might answer him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13084BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13084BK\"></sup>that we might confront each other in court.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13084BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13084BL\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>If only there were someone to mediate between us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13085BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13085BM\"></sup>someone to bring us together,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13085BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13085BN\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>someone to remove God’s rod from me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13086BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13086BO\"></sup>so that his terror would frighten me no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13086BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13086BP\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then I would speak up without fear of him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13087BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13087BQ\"></sup>but as it now stands with me, I cannot.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13087BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13087BR\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>“I loathe my very life;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13088A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13088A\"></sup>therefore I will give free rein to my complaintand speak out in the bitterness of my soul.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13088B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13088B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I say to God:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13089C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13089C\"></sup> Do not declare me guilty,but tell me what charges<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13089D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13089D\"></sup> you have against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13089E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13089E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Does it please you to oppress me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13090F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13090F\"></sup>to spurn the work of your hands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13090G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13090G\"></sup>while you smile on the plans of the wicked?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13090H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13090H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Do you have eyes of flesh?Do you see as a mortal sees?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13091I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13091I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Are your days like those of a mortalor your years like those of a strong man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13092J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13092J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>that you must search out my faultsand probe after my sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13093K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13093K\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>though you know that I am not guilty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13094L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13094L\"></sup>and that no one can rescue me from your hand?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13094M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13094M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Your hands shaped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13095N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13095N\"></sup> me and made me.Will you now turn and destroy me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13095O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13095O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Remember that you molded me like clay.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13096P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13096P\"></sup>Will you now turn me to dust again?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13096Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13096Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Did you not pour me out like milkand curdle me like cheese,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>clothe me with skin and fleshand knit me together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13098R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13098R\"></sup> with bones and sinews?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You gave me life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13099S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13099S\"></sup> and showed me kindness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13099T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13099T\"></sup>and in your providence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13099U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13099U\"></sup> watched over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13099V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13099V\"></sup> my spirit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But this is what you concealed in your heart,and I know that this was in your mind:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13100W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13100W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I sinned, you would be watching me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13101X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13101X\"></sup>and would not let my offense go unpunished.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13101Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13101Y\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If I am guilty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13102Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13102Z\"></sup>—woe to me!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13102AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13102AA\"></sup>Even if I am innocent, I cannot lift my head,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13102AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13102AB\"></sup>for I am full of shameand drowned in my affliction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13102AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13102AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If I hold my head high, you stalk me like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13103AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13103AD\"></sup>and again display your awesome power against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13103AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13103AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You bring new witnesses against me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13104AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13104AF\"></sup>and increase your anger toward me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13104AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13104AG\"></sup>your forces come against me wave upon wave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13104AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13104AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Why then did you bring me out of the womb?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13105AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13105AI\"></sup>I wish I had died before any eye saw me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13105AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13105AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If only I had never come into being,or had been carried straight from the womb to the grave!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13106AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13106AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Are not my few days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13107AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13107AL\"></sup> almost over?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13107AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13107AM\"></sup>Turn away from me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13107AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13107AN\"></sup> so I can have a moment’s joy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13107AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13107AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>before I go to the place of no return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13108AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13108AP\"></sup>to the land of gloom and utter darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13108AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13108AQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>to the land of deepest night,of utter darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13109AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13109AR\"></sup> and disorder,where even the light is like darkness.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13109AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13109AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then Zophar the Naamathite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13110A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13110A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Are all these words to go unanswered?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13111B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13111B\"></sup>Is this talker to be vindicated?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13111C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13111C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Will your idle talk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13112D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13112D\"></sup> reduce others to silence?Will no one rebuke you when you mock?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13112E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13112E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You say to God, ‘My beliefs are flawless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13113F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13113F\"></sup>and I am pure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13113G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13113G\"></sup> in your sight.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Oh, how I wish that God would speak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13114H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13114H\"></sup>that he would open his lips against you",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and disclose to you the secrets of wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13115I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13115I\"></sup>for true wisdom has two sides.Know this: God has even forgotten some of your sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13115J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13115J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Can you fathom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13116K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13116K\"></sup> the mysteries of God?Can you probe the limits of the Almighty?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They are higher<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13117L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13117L\"></sup> than the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13117M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13117M\"></sup> above—what can you do?They are deeper than the depths below<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13117N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13117N\"></sup>—what can you know?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13117O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13117O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their measure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13118P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13118P\"></sup> is longer than the earthand wider than the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13118Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13118Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“If he comes along and confines you in prisonand convenes a court, who can oppose him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13119R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13119R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Surely he recognizes deceivers;and when he sees evil, does he not take note?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13120S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13120S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But the witless can no more become wisethan a wild donkey’s colt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13121T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13121T\"></sup> can be born human.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13121U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13121U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Yet if you devote your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13122V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13122V\"></sup> to himand stretch out your hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13122W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13122W\"></sup> to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13122X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13122X\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>if you put away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13123Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13123Y\"></sup> the sin that is in your handand allow no evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13123Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13123Z\"></sup> to dwell in your tent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13123AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13123AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>then, free of fault, you will lift up your face;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13124AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13124AB\"></sup>you will stand firm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13124AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13124AC\"></sup> and without fear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13124AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13124AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will surely forget your trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13125AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13125AE\"></sup>recalling it only as waters gone by.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13125AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13125AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Life will be brighter than noonday,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13126AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13126AG\"></sup>and darkness will become like morning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13126AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13126AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>You will be secure, because there is hope;you will look about you and take your rest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13127AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13127AI\"></sup> in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13127AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13127AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will lie down, with no one to make you afraid,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13128AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13128AK\"></sup>and many will court your favor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13128AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13128AL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But the eyes of the wicked will fail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13129AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13129AM\"></sup>and escape will elude them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13129AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13129AN\"></sup>their hope will become a dying gasp.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13129AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13129AO\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Doubtless you are the only people who matter,and wisdom will die with you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13131A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13131A\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I have a mind as well as you;I am not inferior to you.Who does not know all these things?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13132B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I have become a laughingstock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13133C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13133C\"></sup> to my friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13133D\"></sup>though I called on God and he answered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13133E\"></sup>—a mere laughingstock, though righteous and blameless!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13133F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13133F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who are at ease have contempt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13134G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13134G\"></sup> for misfortuneas the fate of those whose feet are slipping.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13134H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13134H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The tents of marauders are undisturbed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13135I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13135I\"></sup>and those who provoke God are secure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13135J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13135J\"></sup>—those God has in his hand.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“But ask the animals, and they will teach you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13136K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13136K\"></sup>or the birds in the sky,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13136L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13136L\"></sup> and they will tell you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13136M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13136M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>or speak to the earth, and it will teach you,or let the fish in the sea inform you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Which of all these does not know<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13138N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13138N\"></sup>that the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13138O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13138O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>In his hand is the life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13139P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13139P\"></sup> of every creatureand the breath of all mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13139Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13139Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Does not the ear test wordsas the tongue tastes food?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13140R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13140R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Is not wisdom found among the aged?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13141S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13141S\"></sup>Does not long life bring understanding?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13141T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13141T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“To God belong wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13142U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13142U\"></sup> and power;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13142V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13142V\"></sup>counsel and understanding are his.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13142W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13142W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>What he tears down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13143X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13143X\"></sup> cannot be rebuilt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13143Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13143Y\"></sup>those he imprisons cannot be released.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13143Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13143Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If he holds back the waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13144AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13144AA\"></sup> there is drought;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13144AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13144AB\"></sup>if he lets them loose, they devastate the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13144AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13144AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>To him belong strength and insight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13145AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13145AD\"></sup>both deceived and deceiver are his.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13145AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13145AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He leads rulers away stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13146AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13146AF\"></sup>and makes fools of judges.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13146AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13146AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He takes off the shackles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13147AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13147AH\"></sup> put on by kingsand ties a loincloth around their waist.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13147AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13147AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He leads priests away stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13148AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13148AJ\"></sup>and overthrows officials long established.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13148AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13148AK\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He silences the lips of trusted advisersand takes away the discernment of elders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13149AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13149AL\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>He pours contempt on nobles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13150AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13150AM\"></sup>and disarms the mighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13150AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13150AN\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He reveals the deep things of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13151AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13151AO\"></sup>and brings utter darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13151AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13151AP\"></sup> into the light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13151AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13151AQ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He makes nations great, and destroys them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13152AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13152AR\"></sup>he enlarges nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13152AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13152AS\"></sup> and disperses them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13152AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13152AT\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He deprives the leaders of the earth of their reason;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13153AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13153AU\"></sup>he makes them wander in a trackless waste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13153AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13153AV\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They grope in darkness with no light;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13154AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13154AW\"></sup>he makes them stagger like drunkards.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13154AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13154AX\"></sup>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>“My eyes have seen all this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13155A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13155A\"></sup>my ears have heard and understood it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>What you know, I also know;I am not inferior to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13156B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13156B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I desire to speak to the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13157C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13157C\"></sup>and to argue my case with God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13157D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13157D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You, however, smear me with lies;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13158E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13158E\"></sup>you are worthless physicians,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13158F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13158F\"></sup> all of you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13158G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13158G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If only you would be altogether silent!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13159H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13159H\"></sup>For you, that would be wisdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13159I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13159I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Hear now my argument;listen to the pleas of my lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13160J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13160J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Will you speak wickedly on God’s behalf?Will you speak deceitfully for him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13161K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13161K\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Will you show him partiality?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13162L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13162L\"></sup>Will you argue the case for God?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Would it turn out well if he examined you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13163M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13163M\"></sup>Could you deceive him as you might deceive a mortal?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13163N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13163N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He would surely call you to accountif you secretly showed partiality.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13164O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13164O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Would not his splendor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13165P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13165P\"></sup> terrify you?Would not the dread of him fall on you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13165Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13165Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Your maxims are proverbs of ashes;your defenses are defenses of clay.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13166R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13166R\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Keep silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13167S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13167S\"></sup> and let me speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13167T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13167T\"></sup>then let come to me what may.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13167U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13167U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Why do I put myself in jeopardyand take my life in my hands?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13168V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13168V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Though he slay me, yet will I hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13169W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13169W\"></sup> in him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13169X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13169X\"></sup>I will surely defend my ways to his face.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13169Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13169Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Indeed, this will turn out for my deliverance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13170Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13170Z\"></sup>for no godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13170AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13170AA\"></sup> person would dare come before him!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13170AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13170AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Listen carefully to what I say;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13171AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13171AC\"></sup>let my words ring in your ears.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now that I have prepared my case,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13172AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13172AD\"></sup>I know I will be vindicated.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13172AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13172AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Can anyone bring charges against me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13173AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13173AF\"></sup>If so, I will be silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13173AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13173AG\"></sup> and die.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13173AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13173AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Only grant me these two things, God,and then I will not hide from you:",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Withdraw your hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13175AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13175AI\"></sup> far from me,and stop frightening me with your terrors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13175AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13175AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then summon me and I will answer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13176AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13176AK\"></sup>or let me speak, and you reply to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13176AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13176AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>How many wrongs and sins have I committed?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13177AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13177AM\"></sup>Show me my offense and my sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13177AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13177AN\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Why do you hide your face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13178AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13178AO\"></sup>and consider me your enemy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13178AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13178AP\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Will you torment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13179AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13179AQ\"></sup> a windblown leaf?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13179AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13179AR\"></sup>Will you chase<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13179AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13179AS\"></sup> after dry chaff?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13179AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13179AT\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For you write down bitter things against meand make me reap the sins of my youth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13180AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13180AU\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You fasten my feet in shackles;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13181AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13181AV\"></sup>you keep close watch on all my paths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13181AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13181AW\"></sup>by putting marks on the soles of my feet.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“So man wastes away like something rotten,like a garment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13182AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13182AX\"></sup> eaten by moths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13182AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13182AY\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>“Mortals, born of woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13183A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13183A\"></sup>are of few days<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13183B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13183B\"></sup> and full of trouble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13183C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13183C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They spring up like flowers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13184D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13184D\"></sup> and wither away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13184E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13184E\"></sup>like fleeting shadows,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13184F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13184F\"></sup> they do not endure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13184G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13184G\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do you fix your eye on them?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13185H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13185H\"></sup>Will you bring them before you for judgment?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13185I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13185I\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who can bring what is pure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13186J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13186J\"></sup> from the impure?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13186K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13186K\"></sup>No one!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13186L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13186L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A person’s days are determined;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13187M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13187M\"></sup>you have decreed the number of his months<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13187N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13187N\"></sup>and have set limits he cannot exceed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13187O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13187O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So look away from him and let him alone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13188P\"></sup>till he has put in his time like a hired laborer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13188Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13188Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“At least there is hope for a tree:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13189R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13189R\"></sup>If it is cut down, it will sprout again,and its new shoots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13189S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13189S\"></sup> will not fail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13189T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13189T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Its roots may grow old in the groundand its stump<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13190U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13190U\"></sup> die in the soil,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>yet at the scent of water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13191V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13191V\"></sup> it will budand put forth shoots like a plant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13191W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13191W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But a man dies and is laid low;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13192X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13192X\"></sup>he breathes his last and is no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13192Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13192Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As the water of a lake dries upor a riverbed becomes parched and dry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13193Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13193Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>so he lies down and does not rise;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13194AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13194AA\"></sup>till the heavens are no more,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13194AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13194AB\"></sup> people will not awakeor be roused from their sleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13194AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13194AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If only you would hide me in the grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13195AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13195AD\"></sup>and conceal me till your anger has passed!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13195AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13195AE\"></sup>If only you would set me a timeand then remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13195AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13195AF\"></sup> me!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13195AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13195AG\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If someone dies, will they live again?All the days of my hard service<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13196AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13196AH\"></sup>I will wait for my renewal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13196AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13196AI\"></sup> to come.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You will call and I will answer you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13197AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13197AJ\"></sup>you will long for the creature your hands have made.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13197AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13197AK\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Surely then you will count my steps<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13198AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13198AL\"></sup>but not keep track of my sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13198AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13198AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My offenses will be sealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13199AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13199AN\"></sup> up in a bag;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13199AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13199AO\"></sup>you will cover over my sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13199AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13199AP\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But as a mountain erodes and crumbles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13200AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13200AQ\"></sup>and as a rock is moved from its place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13200AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13200AR\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>as water wears away stonesand torrents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13201AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13201AS\"></sup> wash away the soil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13201AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13201AT\"></sup>so you destroy a person’s hope.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13201AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13201AU\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>You overpower them once for all, and they are gone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13202AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13202AV\"></sup>you change their countenance and send them away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13202AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13202AW\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>If their children are honored, they do not know it;if their offspring are brought low, they do not see it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13203AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13203AX\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They feel but the pain of their own bodies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13204AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13204AY\"></sup>and mourn only for themselves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13204AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13204AZ\"></sup>”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13205A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13205A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Would a wise person answer with empty notionsor fill their belly with the hot east wind?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13206B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13206B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Would they argue with useless words,with speeches that have no value?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13207C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13207C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But you even undermine pietyand hinder devotion to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13208D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13208D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your sin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13209E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13209E\"></sup> prompts your mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13209F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13209F\"></sup>you adopt the tongue of the crafty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13209G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13209G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Your own mouth condemns you, not mine;your own lips testify against you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13210H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13210H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Are you the first man ever born?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13211I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13211I\"></sup>Were you brought forth before the hills?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13211J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13211J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do you listen in on God’s council?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13212K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13212K\"></sup>Do you have a monopoly on wisdom?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13212L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13212L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>What do you know that we do not know?What insights do you have that we do not have?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13213M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13213M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The gray-haired and the aged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13214N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13214N\"></sup> are on our side,men even older than your father.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13214O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13214O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Are God’s consolations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13215P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13215P\"></sup> not enough for you,words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13215Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13215Q\"></sup> spoken gently to you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13215R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13215R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Why has your heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13216S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13216S\"></sup> carried you away,and why do your eyes flash,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>so that you vent your rage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13217T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13217T\"></sup> against Godand pour out such words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13217U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13217U\"></sup> from your mouth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13217V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13217V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“What are mortals, that they could be pure,or those born of woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13218W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13218W\"></sup> that they could be righteous?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13218X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13218X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If God places no trust in his holy ones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13219Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13219Y\"></sup>if even the heavens are not pure in his eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13219Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13219Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>how much less mortals, who are vile and corrupt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13220AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13220AA\"></sup>who drink up evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13220AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13220AB\"></sup> like water!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13220AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13220AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Listen to me and I will explain to you;let me tell you what I have seen,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13221AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13221AD\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>what the wise have declared,hiding nothing received from their ancestors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13222AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13222AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>(to whom alone the land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13223AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13223AF\"></sup> was givenwhen no foreigners moved among them):",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>All his days the wicked man suffers torment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13224AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13224AG\"></sup>the ruthless man through all the years stored up for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13224AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13224AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Terrifying sounds fill his ears;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13225AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13225AI\"></sup>when all seems well, marauders attack him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13225AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13225AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>He despairs of escaping the realm of darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13226AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13226AK\"></sup>he is marked for the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13226AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13226AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He wanders about<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13227AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13227AM\"></sup> for food like a vulture;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13227AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13227AN\"></sup>he knows the day of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13227AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13227AO\"></sup> is at hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13227AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13227AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Distress and anguish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13228AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13228AQ\"></sup> fill him with terror;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13228AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13228AR\"></sup>troubles overwhelm him, like a king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13228AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13228AS\"></sup> poised to attack,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>because he shakes his fist<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13229AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13229AT\"></sup> at Godand vaunts himself against the Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13229AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13229AU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>defiantly charging against himwith a thick, strong shield.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13230AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13230AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Though his face is covered with fatand his waist bulges with flesh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13231AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13231AW\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>he will inhabit ruined townsand houses where no one lives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13232AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13232AX\"></sup>houses crumbling to rubble.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13232AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13232AY\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He will no longer be rich and his wealth will not endure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13233AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13233AZ\"></sup>nor will his possessions spread over the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13233BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13233BA\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He will not escape the darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13234BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13234BB\"></sup>a flame<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13234BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13234BC\"></sup> will wither his shoots,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13234BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13234BD\"></sup>and the breath of God’s mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13234BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13234BE\"></sup> will carry him away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13234BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13234BF\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Let him not deceive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13235BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13235BG\"></sup> himself by trusting what is worthless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13235BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13235BH\"></sup>for he will get nothing in return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13235BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13235BI\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Before his time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13236BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13236BJ\"></sup> he will wither,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13236BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13236BK\"></sup>and his branches will not flourish.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13236BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13236BL\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He will be like a vine stripped of its unripe grapes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13237BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13237BM\"></sup>like an olive tree shedding its blossoms.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13237BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13237BN\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For the company of the godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13238BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13238BO\"></sup> will be barren,and fire will consume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13238BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13238BP\"></sup> the tents of those who love bribes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13238BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13238BQ\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>They conceive trouble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13239BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13239BR\"></sup> and give birth to evil;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13239BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13239BS\"></sup>their womb fashions deceit.”"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I have heard many things like these;you are miserable comforters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13241A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13241A\"></sup> all of you!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13241B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13241B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Will your long-winded speeches never end?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13242C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13242C\"></sup>What ails you that you keep on arguing?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13242D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13242D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I also could speak like you,if you were in my place;I could make fine speeches against youand shake my head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13243E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13243E\"></sup> at you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But my mouth would encourage you;comfort<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13244F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13244F\"></sup> from my lips would bring you relief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13244G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13244G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Yet if I speak, my pain is not relieved;and if I refrain, it does not go away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13245H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13245H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Surely, God, you have worn me out;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13246I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13246I\"></sup>you have devastated my entire household.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13246J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13246J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You have shriveled me up—and it has become a witness;my gauntness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13247K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13247K\"></sup> rises up and testifies against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13247L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13247L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>God assails me and tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13248M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13248M\"></sup> me in his anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13248N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13248N\"></sup>and gnashes his teeth at me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13248O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13248O\"></sup>my opponent fastens on me his piercing eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13248P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13248P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>People open their mouths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13249Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13249Q\"></sup> to jeer at me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13249R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13249R\"></sup>they strike my cheek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13249S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13249S\"></sup> in scornand unite together against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13249T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13249T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>God has turned me over to the ungodlyand thrown me into the clutches of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13250U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13250U\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>All was well with me, but he shattered me;he seized me by the neck and crushed me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13251V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13251V\"></sup>He has made me his target;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13251W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13251W\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>his archers surround me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13252X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13252X\"></sup>Without pity, he pierces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13252Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13252Y\"></sup> my kidneysand spills my gall on the ground.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Again and again<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13253Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13253Z\"></sup> he bursts upon me;he rushes at me like a warrior.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13253AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13253AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I have sewed sackcloth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13254AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13254AB\"></sup> over my skinand buried my brow in the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13254AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13254AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>My face is red with weeping,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13255AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13255AD\"></sup>dark shadows ring my eyes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13255AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13255AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>yet my hands have been free of violence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13256AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13256AF\"></sup>and my prayer is pure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13256AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13256AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Earth, do not cover my blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13257AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13257AH\"></sup>may my cry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13257AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13257AI\"></sup> never be laid to rest!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13257AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13257AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Even now my witness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13258AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13258AK\"></sup> is in heaven;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13258AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13258AL\"></sup>my advocate is on high.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13258AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13258AM\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My intercessor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13259AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13259AN\"></sup> is my friend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13259AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13259AO\"></sup>as my eyes pour out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13259AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13259AP\"></sup> tears<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13259AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13259AQ\"></sup> to God;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>on behalf of a man he pleads<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13260AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13260AR\"></sup> with Godas one pleads for a friend.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Only a few years will passbefore I take the path of no return.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13261AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13261AS\"></sup>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">1 </sup>My spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13262A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13262A\"></sup> is broken,my days are cut short,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13262B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13262B\"></sup>the grave awaits me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13262C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13262C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Surely mockers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13263D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13263D\"></sup> surround me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13263E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13263E\"></sup>my eyes must dwell on their hostility.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Give me, O God, the pledge you demand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13264F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13264F\"></sup>Who else will put up security<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13264G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13264G\"></sup> for me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13264H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13264H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You have closed their minds to understanding;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13265I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13265I\"></sup>therefore you will not let them triumph.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If anyone denounces their friends for reward,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13266J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13266J\"></sup>the eyes of their children will fail.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13266K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13266K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“God has made me a byword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13267L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13267L\"></sup> to everyone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13267M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13267M\"></sup>a man in whose face people spit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13267N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13267N\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My eyes have grown dim with grief;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13268O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13268O\"></sup>my whole frame is but a shadow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13268P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13268P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The upright are appalled at this;the innocent are aroused<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13269Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13269Q\"></sup> against the ungodly.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Nevertheless, the righteous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13270R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13270R\"></sup> will hold to their ways,and those with clean hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13270S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13270S\"></sup> will grow stronger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13270T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13270T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“But come on, all of you, try again!I will not find a wise man among you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13271U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13271U\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My days have passed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13272V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13272V\"></sup> my plans are shattered.Yet the desires of my heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13272W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13272W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>turn night into day;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13273X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13273X\"></sup>in the face of the darkness light is near.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13273Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13273Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If the only home I hope for is the grave,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13274Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13274Z\"></sup>if I spread out my bed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13274AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13274AA\"></sup> in the realm of darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13274AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13274AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>if I say to corruption,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13275AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13275AC\"></sup> ‘You are my father,’and to the worm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13275AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13275AD\"></sup> ‘My mother’ or ‘My sister,’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>where then is my hope—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13276AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13276AE\"></sup>who can see any hope for me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13276AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13276AF\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Will it go down to the gates of death?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13277AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13277AG\"></sup>Will we descend together into the dust?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13277AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13277AH\"></sup>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13278A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13278A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“When will you end these speeches?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13279B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13279B\"></sup>Be sensible, and then we can talk.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Why are we regarded as cattle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13280C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13280C\"></sup>and considered stupid in your sight?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13280D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13280D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You who tear yourself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13281E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13281E\"></sup> to pieces in your anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13281F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13281F\"></sup>is the earth to be abandoned for your sake?Or must the rocks be moved from their place?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13281G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13281G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The lamp of a wicked man is snuffed out;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13282H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13282H\"></sup>the flame of his fire stops burning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13282I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13282I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The light in his tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13283J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13283J\"></sup> becomes dark;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13283K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13283K\"></sup>the lamp beside him goes out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13283L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13283L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The vigor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13284M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13284M\"></sup> of his step is weakened;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13284N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13284N\"></sup>his own schemes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13284O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13284O\"></sup> throw him down.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13284P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13284P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>His feet thrust him into a net;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13285Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13285Q\"></sup>he wanders into its mesh.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A trap seizes him by the heel;a snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13286R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13286R\"></sup> holds him fast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13286S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13286S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>A noose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13287T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13287T\"></sup> is hidden for him on the ground;a trap<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13287U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13287U\"></sup> lies in his path.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13287V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13287V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13288W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13288W\"></sup> startle him on every side<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13288X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13288X\"></sup>and dog<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13288Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13288Y\"></sup> his every step.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Calamity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13289Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13289Z\"></sup> is hungry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13289AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13289AA\"></sup> for him;disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13289AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13289AB\"></sup> is ready for him when he falls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13289AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13289AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It eats away parts of his skin;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13290AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13290AD\"></sup>death’s firstborn devours his limbs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13290AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13290AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He is torn from the security of his tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13291AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13291AF\"></sup>and marched off to the king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13291AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13291AG\"></sup> of terrors.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13291AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13291AH\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Fire resides in his tent;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13292AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13292AI\"></sup>burning sulfur<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13292AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13292AJ\"></sup> is scattered over his dwelling.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>His roots dry up below<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13293AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13293AK\"></sup>and his branches wither above.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13293AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13293AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The memory of him perishes from the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13294AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13294AM\"></sup>he has no name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13294AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13294AN\"></sup> in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13294AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13294AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He is driven from light into the realm of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13295AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13295AP\"></sup>and is banished<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13295AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13295AQ\"></sup> from the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13295AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13295AR\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He has no offspring<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13296AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13296AS\"></sup> or descendants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13296AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13296AT\"></sup> among his people,no survivor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13296AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13296AU\"></sup> where once he lived.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13296AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13296AV\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>People of the west are appalled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13297AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13297AW\"></sup> at his fate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13297AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13297AX\"></sup>those of the east are seized with horror.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Surely such is the dwelling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13298AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13298AY\"></sup> of an evil man;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13298AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13298AZ\"></sup>such is the place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13298BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13298BA\"></sup> of one who does not know God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13298BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13298BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How long will you torment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13300A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13300A\"></sup> meand crush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13300B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13300B\"></sup> me with words?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Ten times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13301C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13301C\"></sup> now you have reproached<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13301D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13301D\"></sup> me;shamelessly you attack me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If it is true that I have gone astray,my error<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13302E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13302E\"></sup> remains my concern alone.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If indeed you would exalt yourselves above me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13303F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13303F\"></sup>and use my humiliation against me,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>then know that God has wronged me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13304G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13304G\"></sup>and drawn his net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13304H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13304H\"></sup> around me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13304I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13304I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Though I cry, ‘Violence!’ I get no response;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13305J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13305J\"></sup>though I call for help,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13305K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13305K\"></sup> there is no justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13305L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13305L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He has blocked my way so I cannot pass;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13306M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13306M\"></sup>he has shrouded my paths in darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13306N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13306N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He has stripped<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13307O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13307O\"></sup> me of my honor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13307P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13307P\"></sup>and removed the crown from my head.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13307Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13307Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He tears me down<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13308R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13308R\"></sup> on every side till I am gone;he uproots my hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13308S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13308S\"></sup> like a tree.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13308T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13308T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>His anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13309U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13309U\"></sup> burns against me;he counts me among his enemies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13309V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13309V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His troops advance in force;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13310W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13310W\"></sup>they build a siege ramp<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13310X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13310X\"></sup> against meand encamp around my tent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13310Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13310Y\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“He has alienated my family<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13311Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13311Z\"></sup> from me;my acquaintances are completely estranged from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13311AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13311AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My relatives have gone away;my closest friends<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13312AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13312AB\"></sup> have forgotten me.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>My guests<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13313AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13313AC\"></sup> and my female servants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13313AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13313AD\"></sup> count me a foreigner;they look on me as on a stranger.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I summon my servant, but he does not answer,though I beg him with my own mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My breath is offensive to my wife;I am loathsome<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13315AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13315AE\"></sup> to my own family.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Even the little boys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13316AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13316AF\"></sup> scorn me;when I appear, they ridicule me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13316AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13316AG\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>All my intimate friends<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13317AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13317AH\"></sup> detest me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13317AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13317AI\"></sup>those I love have turned against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13317AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13317AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I am nothing but skin and bones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13318AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13318AK\"></sup>I have escaped only by the skin of my teeth.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Have pity on me, my friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13319AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13319AL\"></sup> have pity,for the hand of God has struck<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13319AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13319AM\"></sup> me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Why do you pursue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13320AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13320AN\"></sup> me as God does?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13320AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13320AO\"></sup>Will you never get enough of my flesh?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13320AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13320AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Oh, that my words were recorded,that they were written on a scroll,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13321AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13321AQ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>that they were inscribed with an iron tool<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13322AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13322AR\"></sup> on lead,or engraved in rock forever!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13322AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13322AS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I know that my redeemer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13323AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13323AT\"></sup> lives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13323AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13323AU\"></sup>and that in the end he will stand on the earth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And after my skin has been destroyed,yet in my flesh I will see God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13324AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13324AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>I myself will see himwith my own eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13325AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13325AW\"></sup>—I, and not another.How my heart yearns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13325AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13325AX\"></sup> within me!",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“If you say, ‘How we will hound<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13326AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13326AY\"></sup> him,since the root of the trouble lies in him,’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>you should fear the sword yourselves;for wrath will bring punishment by the sword,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13327AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13327AZ\"></sup>and then you will know that there is judgment.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13327BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13327BA\"></sup>"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Then Zophar the Naamathite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13328A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13328A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“My troubled thoughts prompt me to answerbecause I am greatly disturbed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13329B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13329B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I hear a rebuke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13330C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13330C\"></sup> that dishonors me,and my understanding inspires me to reply.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Surely you know how it has been from of old,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13331D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13331D\"></sup>ever since mankind was placed on the earth,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>that the mirth of the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13332E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13332E\"></sup> is brief,the joy of the godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13332F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13332F\"></sup> lasts but a moment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13332G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13332G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Though the pride<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13333H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13333H\"></sup> of the godless person reaches to the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13333I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13333I\"></sup>and his head touches the clouds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13333J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13333J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>he will perish forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13334K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13334K\"></sup> like his own dung;those who have seen him will say, ‘Where is he?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13334L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13334L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like a dream<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13335M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13335M\"></sup> he flies away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13335N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13335N\"></sup> no more to be found,banished<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13335O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13335O\"></sup> like a vision of the night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13335P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13335P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The eye that saw him will not see him again;his place will look on him no more.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13336Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13336Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>His children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13337R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13337R\"></sup> must make amends to the poor;his own hands must give back his wealth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13337S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13337S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The youthful vigor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13338T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13338T\"></sup> that fills his bones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13338U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13338U\"></sup>will lie with him in the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13338V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13338V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Though evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13339W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13339W\"></sup> is sweet in his mouthand he hides it under his tongue,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13339X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13339X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>though he cannot bear to let it goand lets it linger in his mouth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13340Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13340Y\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>yet his food will turn sour in his stomach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13341Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13341Z\"></sup>it will become the venom of serpents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13341AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13341AA\"></sup> within him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He will spit out the riches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13342AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13342AB\"></sup> he swallowed;God will make his stomach vomit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13342AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13342AC\"></sup> them up.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He will suck the poison<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13343AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13343AD\"></sup> of serpents;the fangs of an adder will kill him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13343AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13343AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He will not enjoy the streams,the rivers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13344AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13344AF\"></sup> flowing with honey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13344AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13344AG\"></sup> and cream.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13344AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13344AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>What he toiled for he must give back uneaten;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13345AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13345AI\"></sup>he will not enjoy the profit from his trading.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13345AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13345AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For he has oppressed the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13346AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13346AK\"></sup> and left them destitute;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13346AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13346AL\"></sup>he has seized houses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13346AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13346AM\"></sup> he did not build.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Surely he will have no respite from his craving;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13347AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13347AN\"></sup>he cannot save himself by his treasure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13347AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13347AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Nothing is left for him to devour;his prosperity will not endure.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13348AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13348AP\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>In the midst of his plenty, distress will overtake him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13349AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13349AQ\"></sup>the full force of misery will come upon him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13349AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13349AR\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When he has filled his belly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13350AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13350AS\"></sup>God will vent his burning anger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13350AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13350AT\"></sup> against himand rain down his blows on him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13350AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13350AU\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Though he flees<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13351AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13351AV\"></sup> from an iron weapon,a bronze-tipped arrow pierces him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13351AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13351AW\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He pulls it out of his back,the gleaming point out of his liver.Terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13352AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13352AX\"></sup> will come over him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13352AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13352AY\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>total darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13353AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13353AZ\"></sup> lies in wait for his treasures.A fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13353BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13353BA\"></sup> unfanned will consume him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13353BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13353BB\"></sup>and devour what is left in his tent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13353BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13353BC\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The heavens will expose his guilt;the earth will rise up against him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13354BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13354BD\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>A flood will carry off his house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13355BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13355BE\"></sup>rushing waters on the day of God’s wrath.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13355BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13355BF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Such is the fate God allots the wicked,the heritage appointed for them by God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13356BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13356BG\"></sup>"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Listen carefully to my words;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13358A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13358A\"></sup>let this be the consolation you give me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13358B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13358B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Bear with me while I speak,and after I have spoken, mock on.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13359C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13359C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Is my complaint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13360D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13360D\"></sup> directed to a human being?Why should I not be impatient?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13360E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Look at me and be appalled;clap your hand over your mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13361F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13361F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When I think about this, I am terrified;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13362G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13362G\"></sup>trembling seizes my body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13362H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13362H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Why do the wicked live on,growing old and increasing in power?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13363I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13363I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They see their children established around them,their offspring before their eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13364J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13364J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Their homes are safe and free from fear;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13365K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13365K\"></sup>the rod of God is not on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13365L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13365L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Their bulls never fail to breed;their cows calve and do not miscarry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13366M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13366M\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They send forth their children as a flock;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13367N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13367N\"></sup>their little ones dance about.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They sing to the music of timbrel and lyre;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13368O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13368O\"></sup>they make merry to the sound of the pipe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13368P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13368P\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They spend their years in prosperity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13369Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13369Q\"></sup>and go down to the grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13369R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13369R\"></sup> in peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13369S\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Yet they say to God, ‘Leave us alone!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13370T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13370T\"></sup>We have no desire to know your ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13370U\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Who is the Almighty, that we should serve him?What would we gain by praying to him?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13371V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13371V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But their prosperity is not in their own hands,so I stand aloof from the plans of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13372W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13372W\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Yet how often is the lamp of the wicked snuffed out?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13373X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13373X\"></sup>How often does calamity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13373Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13373Y\"></sup> come upon them,the fate God allots in his anger?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13373Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13373Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>How often are they like straw before the wind,like chaff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13374AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13374AA\"></sup> swept away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13374AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13374AB\"></sup> by a gale?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13374AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13374AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It is said, ‘God stores up the punishment of the wicked for their children.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13375AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13375AD\"></sup>Let him repay the wicked, so that they themselves will experience it!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13375AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13375AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Let their own eyes see their destruction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13376AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13376AF\"></sup>let them drink<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13376AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13376AG\"></sup> the cup of the wrath of the Almighty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13376AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13376AH\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For what do they care about the families they leave behind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13377AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13377AI\"></sup>when their allotted months<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13377AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13377AJ\"></sup> come to an end?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13377AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13377AK\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Can anyone teach knowledge to God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13378AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13378AL\"></sup>since he judges even the highest?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13378AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13378AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>One person dies in full vigor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13379AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13379AN\"></sup>completely secure and at ease,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13379AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13379AO\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>well nourished<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13380AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13380AP\"></sup> in body,bones<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13380AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13380AQ\"></sup> rich with marrow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13380AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13380AR\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Another dies in bitterness of soul,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13381AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13381AS\"></sup>never having enjoyed anything good.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Side by side they lie in the dust,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13382AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13382AT\"></sup>and worms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13382AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13382AU\"></sup> cover them both.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13382AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13382AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“I know full well what you are thinking,the schemes by which you would wrong me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You say, ‘Where now is the house of the great,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13384AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13384AW\"></sup>the tents where the wicked lived?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13384AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13384AX\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Have you never questioned those who travel?Have you paid no regard to their accounts—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>that the wicked are spared from the day of calamity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13386AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13386AY\"></sup>that they are delivered from the day of wrath?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13386AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13386AZ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Who denounces their conduct to their face?Who repays them for what they have done?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13387BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13387BA\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>They are carried to the grave,and watch is kept over their tombs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13388BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13388BB\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The soil in the valley is sweet to them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13389BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13389BC\"></sup>everyone follows after them,and a countless throng goes before them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13389BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13389BD\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“So how can you console me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13390BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13390BE\"></sup> with your nonsense?Nothing is left of your answers but falsehood!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13390BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13390BF\"></sup>"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then Eliphaz the Temanite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13391A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13391A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Can a man be of benefit to God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13392B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13392B\"></sup>Can even a wise person benefit him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13392C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What pleasure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13393D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13393D\"></sup> would it give the Almighty if you were righteous?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13393E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13393E\"></sup>What would he gain if your ways were blameless?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13393F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13393F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Is it for your piety that he rebukes youand brings charges against you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13394G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13394G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Is not your wickedness great?Are not your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13395H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13395H\"></sup> endless?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13395I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13395I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You demanded security<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13396J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13396J\"></sup> from your relatives for no reason;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13396K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13396K\"></sup>you stripped people of their clothing, leaving them naked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13396L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13396L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You gave no water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13397M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13397M\"></sup> to the wearyand you withheld food from the hungry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13397N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13397N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>though you were a powerful man, owning land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13398O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13398O\"></sup>—an honored man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13398P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13398P\"></sup> living on it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13398Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13398Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And you sent widows<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13399R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13399R\"></sup> away empty-handed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13399S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13399S\"></sup>and broke the strength of the fatherless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13399T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13399T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>That is why snares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13400U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13400U\"></sup> are all around you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13400V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13400V\"></sup>why sudden peril terrifies you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13400W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13400W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>why it is so dark<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13401X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13401X\"></sup> you cannot see,and why a flood of water covers you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13401Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13401Y\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is not God in the heights of heaven?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13402Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13402Z\"></sup>And see how lofty are the highest stars!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yet you say, ‘What does God know?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13403AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13403AA\"></sup>Does he judge through such darkness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13403AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13403AB\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thick clouds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13404AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13404AC\"></sup> veil him, so he does not see us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13404AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13404AD\"></sup>as he goes about in the vaulted heavens.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13404AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13404AE\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Will you keep to the old paththat the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13405AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13405AF\"></sup> have trod?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13405AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13405AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They were carried off before their time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13406AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13406AH\"></sup>their foundations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13406AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13406AI\"></sup> washed away by a flood.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13406AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13406AJ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They said to God, ‘Leave us alone!What can the Almighty do to us?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13407AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13407AK\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Yet it was he who filled their houses with good things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13408AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13408AL\"></sup>so I stand aloof from the plans of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13408AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13408AM\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The righteous see their ruin and rejoice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13409AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13409AN\"></sup>the innocent mock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13409AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13409AO\"></sup> them, saying,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>‘Surely our foes are destroyed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13410AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13410AP\"></sup>and fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13410AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13410AQ\"></sup> devours their wealth.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Submit to God and be at peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13411AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13411AR\"></sup> with him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13411AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13411AS\"></sup>in this way prosperity will come to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13411AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13411AT\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Accept instruction from his mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13412AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13412AU\"></sup>and lay up his words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13412AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13412AV\"></sup> in your heart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13412AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13412AW\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If you return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13413AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13413AX\"></sup> to the Almighty, you will be restored:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13413AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13413AY\"></sup>If you remove wickedness far from your tent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13413AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13413AZ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and assign your nuggets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13414BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13414BA\"></sup> to the dust,your gold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13414BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13414BB\"></sup> of Ophir<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13414BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13414BC\"></sup> to the rocks in the ravines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13414BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13414BD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>then the Almighty will be your gold,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13415BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13415BE\"></sup>the choicest silver for you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13415BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13415BF\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Surely then you will find delight in the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13416BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13416BG\"></sup>and will lift up your face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13416BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13416BH\"></sup> to God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13416BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13416BI\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>You will pray to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13417BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13417BJ\"></sup> and he will hear you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13417BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13417BK\"></sup>and you will fulfill your vows.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13417BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13417BL\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>What you decide on will be done,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13418BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13418BM\"></sup>and light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13418BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13418BN\"></sup> will shine on your ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13418BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13418BO\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>When people are brought low<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13419BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13419BP\"></sup> and you say, ‘Lift them up!’then he will save the downcast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13419BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13419BQ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He will deliver even one who is not innocent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13420BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13420BR\"></sup>who will be delivered through the cleanness of your hands.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13420BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13420BS\"></sup>"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Even today my complaint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13422A\"></sup> is bitter;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13422B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13422B\"></sup>his hand is heavy in spite of my groaning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13422C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13422C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If only I knew where to find him;if only I could go to his dwelling!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13423D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13423D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I would state my case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13424E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13424E\"></sup> before himand fill my mouth with arguments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13424F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13424F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I would find out what he would answer me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13425G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13425G\"></sup>and consider what he would say to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Would he vigorously oppose me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13426H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13426H\"></sup>No, he would not press charges against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13426I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13426I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There the upright<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13427J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13427J\"></sup> can establish their innocence before him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13427K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13427K\"></sup>and there I would be delivered forever from my judge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13427L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13427L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But if I go to the east, he is not there;if I go to the west, I do not find him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When he is at work in the north, I do not see him;when he turns to the south, I catch no glimpse of him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13429M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13429M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But he knows the way that I take;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13430N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13430N\"></sup>when he has tested me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13430O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13430O\"></sup> I will come forth as gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13430P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13430P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My feet have closely followed his steps;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13431Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13431Q\"></sup>I have kept to his way without turning aside.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13431R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13431R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I have not departed from the commands of his lips;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13432S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13432S\"></sup>I have treasured the words of his mouth more than my daily bread.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13432T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13432T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But he stands alone, and who can oppose him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13433U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13433U\"></sup>He does whatever he pleases.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13433V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13433V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He carries out his decree against me,and many such plans he still has in store.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13434W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13434W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>That is why I am terrified before him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13435X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13435X\"></sup>when I think of all this, I fear him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13435Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13435Y\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>God has made my heart faint;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13436Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13436Z\"></sup>the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13436AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13436AA\"></sup> has terrified me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13436AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13436AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Yet I am not silenced by the darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13437AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13437AC\"></sup>by the thick darkness that covers my face."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>“Why does the Almighty not set times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13438A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13438A\"></sup> for judgment?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13438B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13438B\"></sup>Why must those who know him look in vain for such days?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13438C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13438C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>There are those who move boundary stones;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13439D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13439D\"></sup>they pasture flocks they have stolen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13439E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13439E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They drive away the orphan’s donkeyand take the widow’s ox in pledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13440F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13440F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They thrust the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13441G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13441G\"></sup> from the pathand force all the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13441H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13441H\"></sup> of the land into hiding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13441I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13441I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Like wild donkeys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13442J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13442J\"></sup> in the desert,the poor go about their labor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13442K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13442K\"></sup> of foraging food;the wasteland<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13442L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13442L\"></sup> provides food for their children.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They gather fodder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13443M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13443M\"></sup> in the fieldsand glean in the vineyards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13443N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13443N\"></sup> of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13443O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13443O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Lacking clothes, they spend the night naked;they have nothing to cover themselves in the cold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13444P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13444P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They are drenched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13445Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13445Q\"></sup> by mountain rainsand hug<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13445R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13445R\"></sup> the rocks for lack of shelter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13445S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13445S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13446T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13446T\"></sup> child is snatched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13446U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13446U\"></sup> from the breast;the infant of the poor is seized<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13446V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13446V\"></sup> for a debt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13446W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13446W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Lacking clothes, they go about naked;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13447X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13447X\"></sup>they carry the sheaves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13447Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13447Y\"></sup> but still go hungry.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They crush olives among the terraces;they tread the winepresses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13448Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13448Z\"></sup> yet suffer thirst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13448AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13448AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The groans of the dying rise from the city,and the souls of the wounded cry out for help.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13449AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13449AB\"></sup>But God charges no one with wrongdoing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13449AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13449AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“There are those who rebel against the light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13450AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13450AD\"></sup>who do not know its waysor stay in its paths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13450AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13450AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When daylight is gone, the murderer rises up,kills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13451AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13451AF\"></sup> the poor and needy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13451AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13451AG\"></sup>and in the night steals forth like a thief.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13451AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13451AH\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The eye of the adulterer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13452AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13452AI\"></sup> watches for dusk;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13452AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13452AJ\"></sup>he thinks, ‘No eye will see me,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13452AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13452AK\"></sup>and he keeps his face concealed.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In the dark, thieves break into houses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13453AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13453AL\"></sup>but by day they shut themselves in;they want nothing to do with the light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13453AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13453AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For all of them, midnight is their morning;they make friends with the terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13454AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13454AN\"></sup> of darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13454AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13454AO\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Yet they are foam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13455AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13455AP\"></sup> on the surface of the water;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13455AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13455AQ\"></sup>their portion of the land is cursed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13455AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13455AR\"></sup>so that no one goes to the vineyards.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13455AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13455AS\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>As heat and drought snatch away the melted snow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13456AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13456AT\"></sup>so the grave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13456AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13456AU\"></sup> snatches away those who have sinned.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The womb forgets them,the worm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13457AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13457AV\"></sup> feasts on them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13457AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13457AW\"></sup>the wicked are no longer remembered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13457AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13457AX\"></sup>but are broken like a tree.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13457AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13457AY\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They prey on the barren and childless woman,and to the widow they show no kindness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13458AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13458AZ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But God drags away the mighty by his power;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13459BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13459BA\"></sup>though they become established,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13459BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13459BB\"></sup> they have no assurance of life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13459BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13459BC\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He may let them rest in a feeling of security,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13460BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13460BD\"></sup>but his eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13460BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13460BE\"></sup> are on their ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13460BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13460BF\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For a little while they are exalted, and then they are gone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13461BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13461BG\"></sup>they are brought low and gathered up like all others;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13461BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13461BH\"></sup>they are cut off like heads of grain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13461BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13461BI\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“If this is not so, who can prove me falseand reduce my words to nothing?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13462BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13462BJ\"></sup>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>Then Bildad the Shuhite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13463A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13463A\"></sup> replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Dominion and awe belong to God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13464B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13464B\"></sup>he establishes order in the heights of heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13464C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13464C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Can his forces be numbered?On whom does his light not rise?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13465D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13465D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>How then can a mortal be righteous before God?How can one born of woman be pure?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13466E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13466E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>If even the moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13467F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13467F\"></sup> is not brightand the stars are not pure in his eyes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13467G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13467G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>how much less a mortal, who is but a maggot—a human being,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13468H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13468H\"></sup> who is only a worm!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13468I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13468I\"></sup>"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>Then Job replied:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How you have helped the powerless!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13470A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13470A\"></sup>How you have saved the arm that is feeble!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13470B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13470B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>What advice you have offered to one without wisdom!And what great insight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13471C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13471C\"></sup> you have displayed!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who has helped you utter these words?And whose spirit spoke from your mouth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13472D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13472D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The dead are in deep anguish,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13473E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13473E\"></sup>those beneath the waters and all that live in them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The realm of the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13474F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13474F\"></sup> is naked before God;Destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13474G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13474G\"></sup> lies uncovered.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13474H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13474H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He spreads out the northern skies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13475I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13475I\"></sup> over empty space;he suspends the earth over nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13475J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13475J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He wraps up the waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13476K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13476K\"></sup> in his clouds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13476L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13476L\"></sup>yet the clouds do not burst under their weight.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He covers the face of the full moon,spreading his clouds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13477M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13477M\"></sup> over it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He marks out the horizon on the face of the waters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13478N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13478N\"></sup>for a boundary between light and darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13478O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13478O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The pillars of the heavens quake,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13479P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13479P\"></sup>aghast at his rebuke.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>By his power he churned up the sea;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13480Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13480Q\"></sup>by his wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13480R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13480R\"></sup> he cut Rahab<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13480S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13480S\"></sup> to pieces.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>By his breath the skies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13481T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13481T\"></sup> became fair;his hand pierced the gliding serpent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13481U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13481U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And these are but the outer fringe of his works;how faint the whisper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13482V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13482V\"></sup> we hear of him!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13482W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13482W\"></sup>Who then can understand the thunder of his power?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13482X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13482X\"></sup>"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>And Job continued his discourse:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13483A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“As surely as God lives, who has denied me justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13484B\"></sup>the Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13484C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13484C\"></sup> who has made my life bitter,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13484D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13484D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>as long as I have life within me,the breath of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13485E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13485E\"></sup> in my nostrils,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>my lips will not say anything wicked,and my tongue will not utter lies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13486F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13486F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will never admit you are in the right;till I die, I will not deny my integrity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13487G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13487G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will maintain my innocence<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13488H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13488H\"></sup> and never let go of it;my conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13488I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13488I\"></sup> will not reproach me as long as I live.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13488J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13488J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“May my enemy be like the wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13489K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13489K\"></sup>my adversary<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13489L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13489L\"></sup> like the unjust!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For what hope have the godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13490M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13490M\"></sup> when they are cut off,when God takes away their life?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13490N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13490N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Does God listen to their crywhen distress comes upon them?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13491O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13491O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Will they find delight in the Almighty?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13492P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13492P\"></sup>Will they call on God at all times?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will teach you about the power of God;the ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13493Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13493Q\"></sup> of the Almighty I will not conceal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13493R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13493R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You have all seen this yourselves.Why then this meaningless talk?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Here is the fate God allots to the wicked,the heritage a ruthless man receives from the Almighty:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13495S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13495S\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>However many his children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13496T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13496T\"></sup> their fate is the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13496U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13496U\"></sup>his offspring will never have enough to eat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13496V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13496V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The plague will bury those who survive him,and their widows will not weep for them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13497W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13497W\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Though he heaps up silver like dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13498X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13498X\"></sup>and clothes like piles of clay,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13498Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13498Y\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>what he lays up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13499Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13499Z\"></sup> the righteous will wear,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13499AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13499AA\"></sup>and the innocent will divide his silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13499AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13499AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13500AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13500AC\"></sup> he builds is like a moth’s cocoon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13500AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13500AD\"></sup>like a hut<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13500AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13500AE\"></sup> made by a watchman.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He lies down wealthy, but will do so no more;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13501AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13501AF\"></sup>when he opens his eyes, all is gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13501AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13501AG\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13502AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13502AH\"></sup> overtake him like a flood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13502AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13502AI\"></sup>a tempest snatches him away in the night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13502AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13502AJ\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The east wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13503AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13503AK\"></sup> carries him off, and he is gone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13503AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13503AL\"></sup>it sweeps him out of his place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13503AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13503AM\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It hurls itself against him without mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13504AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13504AN\"></sup>as he flees headlong<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13504AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13504AO\"></sup> from its power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13504AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13504AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>It claps its hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13505AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13505AQ\"></sup> in derisionand hisses him out of his place.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13505AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13505AR\"></sup>"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>There is a mine for silverand a place where gold is refined.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13506A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13506A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Iron is taken from the earth,and copper is smelted from ore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13507B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13507B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Mortals put an end to the darkness;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13508C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13508C\"></sup>they search out the farthest recessesfor ore in the blackest darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13508D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13508D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Far from human dwellings they cut a shaft,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13509E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13509E\"></sup>in places untouched by human feet;far from other people they dangle and sway.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The earth, from which food comes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13510F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13510F\"></sup>is transformed below as by fire;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>lapis lazuli<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13511G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13511G\"></sup> comes from its rocks,and its dust contains nuggets of gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13511H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13511H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No bird of prey knows that hidden path,no falcon’s eye has seen it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13512I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13512I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Proud beasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13513J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13513J\"></sup> do not set foot on it,and no lion prowls there.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13513K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13513K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>People assault the flinty rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13514L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13514L\"></sup> with their handsand lay bare the roots of the mountains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13514M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13514M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They tunnel through the rock;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13515N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13515N\"></sup>their eyes see all its treasures.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13515O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13515O\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They search the sources of the rivers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13516P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13516P\"></sup>and bring hidden things<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13516Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13516Q\"></sup> to light.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But where can wisdom be found?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13517R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13517R\"></sup>Where does understanding dwell?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13517S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13517S\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>No mortal comprehends its worth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13518T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13518T\"></sup>it cannot be found in the land of the living.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13518U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13518U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The deep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13519V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13519V\"></sup> says, “It is not in me”;the sea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13519W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13519W\"></sup> says, “It is not with me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>It cannot be bought with the finest gold,nor can its price be weighed out in silver.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13520X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13520X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>It cannot be bought with the gold of Ophir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13521Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13521Y\"></sup>with precious onyx or lapis lazuli.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13521Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13521Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Neither gold nor crystal can compare with it,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13522AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13522AA\"></sup>nor can it be had for jewels of gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13522AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13522AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Coral<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13523AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13523AC\"></sup> and jasper<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13523AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13523AD\"></sup> are not worthy of mention;the price of wisdom is beyond rubies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13523AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13523AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The topaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13524AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13524AF\"></sup> of Cush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13524AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13524AG\"></sup> cannot compare with it;it cannot be bought with pure gold.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13524AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13524AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Where then does wisdom come from?Where does understanding dwell?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13525AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13525AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It is hidden from the eyes of every living thing,concealed even from the birds in the sky.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13526AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13526AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Destruction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13527AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13527AK\"></sup> and Death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13527AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13527AL\"></sup> say,“Only a rumor of it has reached our ears.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>God understands the way to itand he alone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13528AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13528AM\"></sup> knows where it dwells,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13528AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13528AN\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for he views the ends of the earth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13529AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13529AO\"></sup>and sees everything under the heavens.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13529AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13529AP\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When he established the force of the windand measured out the waters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13530AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13530AQ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>when he made a decree for the rain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13531AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13531AR\"></sup>and a path for the thunderstorm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13531AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13531AS\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>then he looked at wisdom and appraised it;he confirmed it and tested it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13532AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13532AT\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to the human race,“The fear of the Lord—that is wisdom,and to shun evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13533AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13533AU\"></sup> is understanding.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13533AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13533AV\"></sup>"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Job continued his discourse:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13534A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13534A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How I long for the months gone by,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13535B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13535B\"></sup>for the days when God watched over me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13535C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13535C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>when his lamp shone on my headand by his light I walked through darkness!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13536D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Oh, for the days when I was in my prime,when God’s intimate friendship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13537E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13537E\"></sup> blessed my house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13537F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13537F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>when the Almighty was still with meand my children<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13538G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13538G\"></sup> were around me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13538H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13538H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>when my path was drenched with cream<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13539I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13539I\"></sup>and the rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13539J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13539J\"></sup> poured out for me streams of olive oil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13539K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13539K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“When I went to the gate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13540L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13540L\"></sup> of the cityand took my seat in the public square,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>the young men saw me and stepped aside<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13541M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13541M\"></sup>and the old men rose to their feet;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13541N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13541N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>the chief men refrained from speaking<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13542O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13542O\"></sup>and covered their mouths with their hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13542P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13542P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the voices of the nobles were hushed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13543Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13543Q\"></sup>and their tongues stuck to the roof of their mouths.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13543R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13543R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Whoever heard me spoke well of me,and those who saw me commended me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13544S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13544S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>because I rescued the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13545T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13545T\"></sup> who cried for help,and the fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13545U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13545U\"></sup> who had none to assist them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13545V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13545V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The one who was dying blessed me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13546W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13546W\"></sup>I made the widow’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13546X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13546X\"></sup> heart sing.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I put on righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13547Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13547Y\"></sup> as my clothing;justice was my robe and my turban.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13547Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13547Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I was eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13548AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13548AA\"></sup> to the blindand feet to the lame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13548AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13548AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I was a father to the needy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13549AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13549AC\"></sup>I took up the case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13549AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13549AD\"></sup> of the stranger.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13549AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13549AE\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I broke the fangs of the wickedand snatched the victims<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13550AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13550AF\"></sup> from their teeth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13550AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13550AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I thought, ‘I will die in my own house,my days as numerous as the grains of sand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13551AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13551AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>My roots will reach to the water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13552AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13552AI\"></sup>and the dew will lie all night on my branches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13552AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13552AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My glory will not fade;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13553AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13553AK\"></sup>the bow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13553AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13553AL\"></sup> will be ever new in my hand.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13553AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13553AM\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“People listened to me expectantly,waiting in silence for my counsel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13554AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13554AN\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>After I had spoken, they spoke no more;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13555AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13555AO\"></sup>my words fell gently on their ears.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13555AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13555AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>They waited for me as for showersand drank in my words as the spring rain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13556AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13556AQ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When I smiled at them, they scarcely believed it;the light of my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13557AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13557AR\"></sup> was precious to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13557AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13557AS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I chose the way for them and sat as their chief;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13558AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13558AT\"></sup>I dwelt as a king<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13558AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13558AU\"></sup> among his troops;I was like one who comforts mourners.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13558AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13558AV\"></sup>"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“But now they mock me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13559A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13559A\"></sup>men younger than I,whose fathers I would have disdainedto put with my sheep dogs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13559B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13559B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Of what use was the strength of their hands to me,since their vigor had gone from them?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Haggard from want and hunger,they roamed the parched land<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13561C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13561C\"></sup>in desolate wastelands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13561D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13561D\"></sup> at night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13561E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13561E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In the brush they gathered salt herbs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13562F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13562F\"></sup>and their food was the root of the broom bush.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13562G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13562G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They were banished from human society,shouted at as if they were thieves.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They were forced to live in the dry stream beds,among the rocks and in holes in the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13564H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13564H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They brayed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13565I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13565I\"></sup> among the bushes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13565J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13565J\"></sup>and huddled in the undergrowth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>A base and nameless brood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13566K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13566K\"></sup>they were driven out of the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13566L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13566L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And now those young men mock me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13567M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13567M\"></sup> in song;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13567N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13567N\"></sup>I have become a byword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13567O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13567O\"></sup> among them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They detest me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13568P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13568P\"></sup> and keep their distance;they do not hesitate to spit in my face.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13568Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13568Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now that God has unstrung my bow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13569R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13569R\"></sup> and afflicted me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13569S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13569S\"></sup>they throw off restraint<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13569T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13569T\"></sup> in my presence.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>On my right<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13570U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13570U\"></sup> the tribe attacks;they lay snares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13570V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13570V\"></sup> for my feet,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13570W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13570W\"></sup>they build their siege ramps against me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13570X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13570X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They break up my road;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13571Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13571Y\"></sup>they succeed in destroying me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13571Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13571Z\"></sup>‘No one can help him,’ they say.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They advance as through a gaping breach;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13572AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13572AA\"></sup>amid the ruins they come rolling in.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Terrors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13573AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13573AB\"></sup> overwhelm me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13573AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13573AC\"></sup>my dignity is driven away as by the wind,my safety vanishes like a cloud.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13573AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13573AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“And now my life ebbs away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13574AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13574AE\"></sup>days of suffering grip me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13574AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13574AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Night pierces my bones;my gnawing pains never rest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13575AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13575AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In his great power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13576AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13576AH\"></sup> God becomes like clothing to me;he binds me like the neck of my garment.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>He throws me into the mud,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13577AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13577AI\"></sup>and I am reduced to dust and ashes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13577AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13577AJ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I cry out to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13578AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13578AK\"></sup> God, but you do not answer;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13578AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13578AL\"></sup>I stand up, but you merely look at me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You turn on me ruthlessly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13579AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13579AM\"></sup>with the might of your hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13579AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13579AN\"></sup> you attack me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13579AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13579AO\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You snatch me up and drive me before the wind;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13580AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13580AP\"></sup>you toss me about in the storm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13580AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13580AQ\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I know you will bring me down to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13581AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13581AR\"></sup>to the place appointed for all the living.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13581AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13581AS\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Surely no one lays a hand on a broken man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13582AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13582AT\"></sup>when he cries for help in his distress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13582AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13582AU\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Have I not wept for those in trouble?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13583AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13583AV\"></sup>Has not my soul grieved for the poor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13583AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13583AW\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Yet when I hoped for good, evil came;when I looked for light, then came darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13584AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13584AX\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The churning inside me never stops;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13585AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13585AY\"></sup>days of suffering confront me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13585AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13585AZ\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>I go about blackened,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13586BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13586BA\"></sup> but not by the sun;I stand up in the assembly and cry for help.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13586BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13586BB\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I have become a brother of jackals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13587BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13587BC\"></sup>a companion of owls.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13587BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13587BD\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>My skin grows black<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13588BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13588BE\"></sup> and peels;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13588BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13588BF\"></sup>my body burns with fever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13588BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13588BG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>My lyre is tuned to mourning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13589BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13589BH\"></sup>and my pipe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13589BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13589BI\"></sup> to the sound of wailing."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>“I made a covenant with my eyes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13590A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13590A\"></sup>not to look lustfully at a young woman.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13590B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13590B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For what is our lot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13591C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13591C\"></sup> from God above,our heritage from the Almighty on high?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13591D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13591D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Is it not ruin<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13592E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13592E\"></sup> for the wicked,disaster<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13592F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13592F\"></sup> for those who do wrong?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13592G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13592G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Does he not see my ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13593H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13593H\"></sup>and count my every step?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13593I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13593I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“If I have walked with falsehoodor my foot has hurried after deceit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13594J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13594J\"></sup>—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>let God weigh me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13595K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13595K\"></sup> in honest scales<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13595L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13595L\"></sup>and he will know that I am blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13595M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13595M\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>if my steps have turned from the path,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13596N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13596N\"></sup>if my heart has been led by my eyes,or if my hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13596O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13596O\"></sup> have been defiled,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13596P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13596P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>then may others eat what I have sown,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13597Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13597Q\"></sup>and may my crops be uprooted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13597R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13597R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“If my heart has been enticed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13598S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13598S\"></sup> by a woman,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13598T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13598T\"></sup>or if I have lurked at my neighbor’s door,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>then may my wife grind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13599U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13599U\"></sup> another man’s grain,and may other men sleep with her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13599V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13599V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For that would have been wicked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13600W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13600W\"></sup>a sin to be judged.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13600X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13600X\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is a fire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13601Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13601Y\"></sup> that burns to Destruction;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13601Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13601Z\"></sup>it would have uprooted my harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13601AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13601AA\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If I have denied justice to any of my servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13602AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13602AB\"></sup>whether male or female,when they had a grievance against me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13602AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13602AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>what will I do when God confronts me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13603AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13603AD\"></sup>What will I answer when called to account?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13603AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13603AE\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Did not he who made me in the womb make them?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13604AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13604AF\"></sup>Did not the same one form us both within our mothers?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13604AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13604AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If I have denied the desires of the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13605AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13605AH\"></sup>or let the eyes of the widow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13605AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13605AI\"></sup> grow weary,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13605AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13605AJ\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>if I have kept my bread to myself,not sharing it with the fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13606AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13606AK\"></sup>—",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>but from my youth I reared them as a father would,and from my birth I guided the widow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13607AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13607AL\"></sup>—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>if I have seen anyone perishing for lack of clothing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13608AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13608AM\"></sup>or the needy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13608AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13608AN\"></sup> without garments,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and their hearts did not bless me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13609AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13609AO\"></sup>for warming them with the fleece<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13609AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13609AP\"></sup> from my sheep,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>if I have raised my hand against the fatherless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13610AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13610AQ\"></sup>knowing that I had influence in court,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13610AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13610AR\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>then let my arm fall from the shoulder,let it be broken off at the joint.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13611AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13611AS\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For I dreaded destruction from God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13612AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13612AT\"></sup>and for fear of his splendor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13612AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13612AU\"></sup> I could not do such things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13612AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13612AV\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“If I have put my trust in gold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13613AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13613AW\"></sup>or said to pure gold, ‘You are my security,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13613AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13613AX\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>if I have rejoiced over my great wealth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13614AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13614AY\"></sup>the fortune my hands had gained,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13614AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13614AZ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>if I have regarded the sun<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13615BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13615BA\"></sup> in its radianceor the moon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13615BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13615BB\"></sup> moving in splendor,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>so that my heart was secretly enticed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13616BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13616BC\"></sup>and my hand offered them a kiss of homage,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13616BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13616BD\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>then these also would be sins to be judged,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13617BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13617BE\"></sup>for I would have been unfaithful to God on high.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13617BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13617BF\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“If I have rejoiced at my enemy’s misfortune<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13618BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13618BG\"></sup>or gloated over the trouble that came to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13618BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13618BH\"></sup>—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I have not allowed my mouth to sinby invoking a curse against their life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13619BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13619BI\"></sup>—",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>if those of my household have never said,‘Who has not been filled with Job’s meat?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13620BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13620BJ\"></sup>—",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>but no stranger had to spend the night in the street,for my door was always open to the traveler<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13621BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13621BK\"></sup>—",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>if I have concealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13622BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13622BL\"></sup> my sin as people do,by hiding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13622BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13622BM\"></sup> my guilt in my heart",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>because I so feared the crowd<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13623BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13623BN\"></sup>and so dreaded the contempt of the clansthat I kept silent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13623BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13623BO\"></sup> and would not go outside—",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>(“Oh, that I had someone to hear me!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13624BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13624BP\"></sup>I sign now my defense—let the Almighty answer me;let my accuser<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13624BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13624BQ\"></sup> put his indictment in writing.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Surely I would wear it on my shoulder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13625BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13625BR\"></sup>I would put it on like a crown.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13625BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13625BS\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I would give him an account of my every step;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13626BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13626BT\"></sup>I would present it to him as to a ruler.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13626BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13626BU\"></sup>)—",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“if my land cries out against me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13627BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13627BV\"></sup>and all its furrows are wet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13627BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13627BW\"></sup> with tears,",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>if I have devoured its yield without payment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13628BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13628BX\"></sup>or broken the spirit of its tenants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13628BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13628BY\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>then let briers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13629BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13629BZ\"></sup> come up instead of wheatand stinkweed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13629CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13629CA\"></sup> instead of barley.”The words of Job are ended.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13629CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13629CB\"></sup>"
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>So these three men stopped answering Job,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13630A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13630A\"></sup> because he was righteous in his own eyes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13630B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13630B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But Elihu son of Barakel the Buzite,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13631C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13631C\"></sup> of the family of Ram, became very angry with Job for justifying himself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13631D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13631D\"></sup> rather than God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13631E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13631E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He was also angry with the three friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13632F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13632F\"></sup> because they had found no way to refute Job,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13632G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13632G\"></sup> and yet had condemned him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13632H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13632H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now Elihu had waited before speaking to Job because they were older than he.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13633I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13633I\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But when he saw that the three men had nothing more to say, his anger was aroused.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So Elihu son of Barakel the Buzite said:“I am young in years,and you are old;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13635J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13635J\"></sup>that is why I was fearful,not daring to tell you what I know.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I thought, ‘Age should speak;advanced years should teach wisdom.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13636K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13636K\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But it is the spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13637L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13637L\"></sup> in a person,the breath of the Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13637M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13637M\"></sup> that gives them understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13637N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13637N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>It is not only the old who are wise,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13638O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13638O\"></sup>not only the aged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13638P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13638P\"></sup> who understand what is right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13638Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13638Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Therefore I say: Listen to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13639R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13639R\"></sup>I too will tell you what I know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13639S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13639S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I waited while you spoke,I listened to your reasoning;while you were searching for words,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>I gave you my full attention.But not one of you has proved Job wrong;none of you has answered his arguments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13641T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13641T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Do not say, ‘We have found wisdom;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13642U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13642U\"></sup>let God, not a man, refute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13642V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13642V\"></sup> him.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Job has not marshaled his words against me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13643W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13643W\"></sup>and I will not answer him with your arguments.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“They are dismayed and have no more to say;words have failed them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13644X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13644X\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Must I wait, now that they are silent,now that they stand there with no reply?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I too will have my say;I too will tell what I know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13646Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13646Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For I am full of words,and the spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13647Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13647Z\"></sup> within me compels me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13647AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13647AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>inside I am like bottled-up wine,like new wineskins ready to burst.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13648AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13648AB\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I must speak and find relief;I must open my lips and reply.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13649AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13649AC\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will show no partiality,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13650AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13650AD\"></sup>nor will I flatter anyone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13650AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13650AE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>for if I were skilled in flattery,my Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13651AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13651AF\"></sup> would soon take me away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13651AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13651AG\"></sup>"
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>“But now, Job, listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13652A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13652A\"></sup> to my words;pay attention to everything I say.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13652B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13652B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I am about to open my mouth;my words are on the tip of my tongue.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>My words come from an upright heart;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13654C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13654C\"></sup>my lips sincerely speak what I know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13654D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13654D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13655E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13655E\"></sup> of God has made me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13655F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13655F\"></sup>the breath of the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13655G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13655G\"></sup> gives me life.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13655H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13655H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Answer me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13656I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13656I\"></sup> then, if you can;stand up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13656J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13656J\"></sup> and argue your case before me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13656K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13656K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I am the same as you in God’s sight;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13657L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13657L\"></sup>I too am a piece of clay.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13657M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13657M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No fear of me should alarm you,nor should my hand be heavy on you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13658N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13658N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But you have said in my hearing—I heard the very words—",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘I am pure,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13660O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13660O\"></sup> I have done no wrong;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13660P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13660P\"></sup>I am clean and free from sin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13660Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13660Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Yet God has found fault with me;he considers me his enemy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13661R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13661R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He fastens my feet in shackles;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13662S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13662S\"></sup>he keeps close watch on all my paths.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13662T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13662T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“But I tell you, in this you are not right,for God is greater than any mortal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13663U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13663U\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Why do you complain to him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13664V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13664V\"></sup>that he responds to no one’s words?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13664W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13664W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For God does speak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13665X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13665X\"></sup>—now one way, now another<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13665Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13665Y\"></sup>—though no one perceives it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13665Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13665Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In a dream,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13666AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13666AA\"></sup> in a vision<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13666AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13666AB\"></sup> of the night,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13666AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13666AC\"></sup>when deep sleep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13666AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13666AD\"></sup> falls on peopleas they slumber in their beds,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>he may speak<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13667AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13667AE\"></sup> in their earsand terrify them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13667AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13667AF\"></sup> with warnings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13667AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13667AG\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>to turn them from wrongdoingand keep them from pride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13668AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13668AH\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>to preserve them from the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13669AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13669AI\"></sup>their lives from perishing by the sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13669AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13669AJ\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Or someone may be chastened<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13670AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13670AK\"></sup> on a bed of pain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13670AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13670AL\"></sup>with constant distress in their bones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13670AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13670AM\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>so that their body finds food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13671AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13671AN\"></sup> repulsiveand their soul loathes the choicest meal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13671AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13671AO\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Their flesh wastes away to nothing,and their bones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13672AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13672AP\"></sup> once hidden, now stick out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13672AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13672AQ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They draw near to the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13673AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13673AR\"></sup>and their life to the messengers of death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13673AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13673AS\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Yet if there is an angel at their side,a messenger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13674AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13674AT\"></sup> one out of a thousand,sent to tell them how to be upright,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13674AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13674AU\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and he is gracious to that person and says to God,‘Spare them from going down to the pit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13675AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13675AV\"></sup>I have found a ransom for them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13675AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13675AW\"></sup>—",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>let their flesh be renewed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13676AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13676AX\"></sup> like a child’s;let them be restored as in the days of their youth’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13676AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13676AY\"></sup>—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>then that person can pray to God and find favor with him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13677AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13677AZ\"></sup>they will see God’s face and shout for joy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13677BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13677BA\"></sup>he will restore them to full well-being.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13677BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13677BB\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And they will go to others and say,‘I have sinned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13678BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13678BC\"></sup> I have perverted what is right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13678BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13678BD\"></sup>but I did not get what I deserved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13678BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13678BE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>God has delivered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13679BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13679BF\"></sup> me from going down to the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13679BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13679BG\"></sup>and I shall live to enjoy the light of life.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13679BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13679BH\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“God does all these things to a person<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13680BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13680BI\"></sup>—twice, even three times<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13680BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13680BJ\"></sup>—",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>to turn them back<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13681BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13681BK\"></sup> from the pit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13681BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13681BL\"></sup>that the light of life<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13681BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13681BM\"></sup> may shine on them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13681BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13681BN\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Pay attention, Job, and listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13682BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13682BO\"></sup> to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13682BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13682BP\"></sup>be silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13682BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13682BQ\"></sup> and I will speak.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If you have anything to say, answer me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13683BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13683BR\"></sup>speak up, for I want to vindicate you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13683BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13683BS\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But if not, then listen to me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13684BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13684BT\"></sup>be silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13684BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13684BU\"></sup> and I will teach you wisdom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13684BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13684BV\"></sup>”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Then Elihu said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Hear my words, you wise men;listen to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13686A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13686A\"></sup> you men of learning.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For the ear tests wordsas the tongue tastes food.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13687B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13687B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let us discern for ourselves what is right;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13688C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13688C\"></sup>let us learn together what is good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13688D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13688D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Job says, ‘I am innocent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13689E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13689E\"></sup>but God denies me justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13689F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13689F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Although I am right,I am considered a liar;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13690G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13690G\"></sup>although I am guiltless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13690H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13690H\"></sup>his arrow inflicts an incurable wound.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13690I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13690I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is there anyone like Job,who drinks scorn like water?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13691J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13691J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He keeps company with evildoers;he associates with the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13692K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13692K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For he says, ‘There is no profitin trying to please God.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13693L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13693L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“So listen to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13694M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13694M\"></sup> you men of understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13694N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13694N\"></sup>Far be it from God to do evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13694O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13694O\"></sup>from the Almighty to do wrong.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13694P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13694P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He repays everyone for what they have done;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13695Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13695Q\"></sup>he brings on them what their conduct deserves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13695R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13695R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It is unthinkable that God would do wrong,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13696S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13696S\"></sup>that the Almighty would pervert justice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13696T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13696T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who appointed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13697U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13697U\"></sup> him over the earth?Who put him in charge of the whole world?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13697V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13697V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If it were his intentionand he withdrew his spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13698W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13698W\"></sup> and breath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13698X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13698X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>all humanity would perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13699Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13699Y\"></sup> togetherand mankind would return to the dust.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13699Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13699Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“If you have understanding,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13700AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13700AA\"></sup> hear this;listen to what I say.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13700AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13700AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Can someone who hates justice govern?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13701AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13701AC\"></sup>Will you condemn the just and mighty One?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13701AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13701AD\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Is he not the One who says to kings, ‘You are worthless,’and to nobles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13702AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13702AE\"></sup> ‘You are wicked,’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13702AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13702AF\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>who shows no partiality<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13703AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13703AG\"></sup> to princesand does not favor the rich over the poor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13703AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13703AH\"></sup>for they are all the work of his hands?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13703AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13703AI\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They die in an instant, in the middle of the night;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13704AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13704AJ\"></sup>the people are shaken and they pass away;the mighty are removed without human hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13704AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13704AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“His eyes are on the ways of mortals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13705AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13705AL\"></sup>he sees their every step.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13705AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13705AM\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>There is no deep shadow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13706AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13706AN\"></sup> no utter darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13706AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13706AO\"></sup>where evildoers can hide.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13706AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13706AP\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>God has no need to examine people further,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13707AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13707AQ\"></sup>that they should come before him for judgment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13707AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13707AR\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Without inquiry he shatters<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13708AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13708AS\"></sup> the mighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13708AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13708AT\"></sup>and sets up others in their place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13708AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13708AU\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Because he takes note of their deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13709AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13709AV\"></sup>he overthrows them in the night<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13709AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13709AW\"></sup> and they are crushed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13709AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13709AX\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He punishes them for their wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13710AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13710AY\"></sup>where everyone can see them,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>because they turned from following him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13711AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13711AZ\"></sup>and had no regard for any of his ways.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13711BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13711BA\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They caused the cry of the poor to come before him,so that he heard the cry of the needy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13712BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13712BB\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But if he remains silent,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13713BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13713BC\"></sup> who can condemn him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13713BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13713BD\"></sup>If he hides his face,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13713BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13713BE\"></sup> who can see him?Yet he is over individual and nation alike,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13713BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13713BF\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>to keep the godless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13714BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13714BG\"></sup> from ruling,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13714BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13714BH\"></sup>from laying snares for the people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13714BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13714BI\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Suppose someone says to God,‘I am guilty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13715BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13715BJ\"></sup> but will offend no more.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Teach me what I cannot see;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13716BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13716BK\"></sup>if I have done wrong, I will not do so again.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13716BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13716BL\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Should God then reward you on your terms,when you refuse to repent?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13717BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13717BM\"></sup>You must decide, not I;so tell me what you know.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Men of understanding declare,wise men who hear me say to me,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>‘Job speaks without knowledge;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13719BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13719BN\"></sup>his words lack insight.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13719BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13719BO\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Oh, that Job might be tested to the utmostfor answering like a wicked man!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13720BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13720BP\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>To his sin he adds rebellion;scornfully he claps his hands<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13721BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13721BQ\"></sup> among usand multiplies his words<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13721BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13721BR\"></sup> against God.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13721BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13721BS\"></sup>"
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>Then Elihu said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Do you think this is just?You say, ‘I am in the right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13723A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13723A\"></sup> not God.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13723B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13723B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Yet you ask him, ‘What profit is it to me,and what do I gain by not sinning?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13724C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13724C\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I would like to reply to youand to your friends with you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Look up at the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13726D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13726D\"></sup> and see;gaze at the clouds so high above you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13726E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13726E\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If you sin, how does that affect him?If your sins are many, what does that do to him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13727F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13727F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If you are righteous, what do you give to him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13728G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13728G\"></sup>or what does he receive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13728H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13728H\"></sup> from your hand?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13728I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13728I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Your wickedness only affects humans like yourself,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13729J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13729J\"></sup>and your righteousness only other people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13729K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13729K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“People cry out<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13730L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13730L\"></sup> under a load of oppression;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13730M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13730M\"></sup>they plead for relief from the arm of the powerful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13730N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13730N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But no one says, ‘Where is God my Maker,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13731O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13731O\"></sup>who gives songs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13731P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13731P\"></sup> in the night,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13731Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13731Q\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>who teaches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13732R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13732R\"></sup> us<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13732S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13732S\"></sup> more than he teaches the beasts of the earthand makes us wiser than the birds in the sky?’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He does not answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13733T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13733T\"></sup> when people cry outbecause of the arrogance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13733U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13733U\"></sup> of the wicked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13733V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13733V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Indeed, God does not listen to their empty plea;the Almighty pays no attention to it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13734W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13734W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>How much less, then, will he listenwhen you say that you do not see him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13735X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13735X\"></sup>that your case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13735Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13735Y\"></sup> is before himand you must wait for him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13735Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13735Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and further, that his anger never punishes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13736AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13736AA\"></sup>and he does not take the least notice of wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13736AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13736AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So Job opens his mouth with empty talk;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13737AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13737AC\"></sup>without knowledge he multiplies words.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13737AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13737AD\"></sup>"
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span>Elihu continued:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Bear with me a little longer and I will show youthat there is more to be said in God’s behalf.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I get my knowledge from afar;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13740A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13740A\"></sup>I will ascribe justice to my Maker.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13740B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13740B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Be assured that my words are not false;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13741C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13741C\"></sup>one who has perfect knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13741D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13741D\"></sup> is with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13741E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13741E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“God is mighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13742F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13742F\"></sup> but despises no one;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13742G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13742G\"></sup>he is mighty, and firm in his purpose.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13742H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13742H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He does not keep the wicked alive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13743I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13743I\"></sup>but gives the afflicted their rights.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13743J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13743J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He does not take his eyes off the righteous;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13744K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13744K\"></sup>he enthrones them with kings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13744L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13744L\"></sup>and exalts them forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13744M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13744M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But if people are bound in chains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13745N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13745N\"></sup>held fast by cords of affliction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13745O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13745O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>he tells them what they have done—that they have sinned arrogantly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13746P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13746P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He makes them listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13747Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13747Q\"></sup> to correction<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13747R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13747R\"></sup>and commands them to repent of their evil.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13747S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13747S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If they obey and serve him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13748T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13748T\"></sup>they will spend the rest of their days in prosperity<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13748U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13748U\"></sup>and their years in contentment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13748V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13748V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But if they do not listen,they will perish by the sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13749W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13749W\"></sup>and die without knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13749X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13749X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The godless in heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13750Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13750Y\"></sup> harbor resentment;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13750Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13750Z\"></sup>even when he fetters them, they do not cry for help.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13750AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13750AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They die in their youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13751AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13751AB\"></sup>among male prostitutes of the shrines.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13751AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13751AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But those who suffer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13752AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13752AD\"></sup> he delivers in their suffering;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13752AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13752AE\"></sup>he speaks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13752AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13752AF\"></sup> to them in their affliction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13752AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13752AG\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“He is wooing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13753AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13753AH\"></sup> you from the jaws of distressto a spacious place<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13753AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13753AI\"></sup> free from restriction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13753AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13753AJ\"></sup>to the comfort of your table<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13753AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13753AK\"></sup> laden with choice food.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13753AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13753AL\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But now you are laden with the judgment due the wicked;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13754AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13754AM\"></sup>judgment and justice have taken hold of you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13754AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13754AN\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Be careful that no one entices you by riches;do not let a large bribe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13755AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13755AO\"></sup> turn you aside.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13755AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13755AP\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Would your wealth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13756AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13756AQ\"></sup> or even all your mighty effortssustain you so you would not be in distress?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do not long for the night,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13757AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13757AR\"></sup>to drag people away from their homes.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Beware of turning to evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13758AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13758AS\"></sup>which you seem to prefer to affliction.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13758AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13758AT\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“God is exalted in his power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13759AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13759AU\"></sup>Who is a teacher like him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13759AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13759AV\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Who has prescribed his ways<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13760AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13760AW\"></sup> for him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13760AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13760AX\"></sup>or said to him, ‘You have done wrong’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13760AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13760AY\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Remember to extol his work,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13761AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13761AZ\"></sup>which people have praised in song.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13761BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13761BA\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>All humanity has seen it;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13762BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13762BB\"></sup>mortals gaze on it from afar.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>How great is God—beyond our understanding!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13763BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13763BC\"></sup>The number of his years is past finding out.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13763BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13763BD\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“He draws up the drops of water,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13764BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13764BE\"></sup>which distill as rain to the streams;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13764BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13764BF\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>the clouds pour down their moistureand abundant showers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13765BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13765BG\"></sup> fall on mankind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13765BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13765BH\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Who can understand how he spreads out the clouds,how he thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13766BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13766BI\"></sup> from his pavilion?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13766BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13766BJ\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>See how he scatters his lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13767BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13767BK\"></sup> about him,bathing the depths of the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13767BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13767BL\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>This is the way he governs the nations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13768BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13768BM\"></sup>and provides food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13768BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13768BN\"></sup> in abundance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13768BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13768BO\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>He fills his hands with lightningand commands it to strike its mark.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13769BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13769BP\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>His thunder announces the coming storm;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13770BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13770BQ\"></sup>even the cattle make known its approach.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13770BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13770BR\"></sup>"
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>“At this my heart pounds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13771A\"></sup>and leaps from its place.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Listen!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13772B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13772B\"></sup> Listen to the roar of his voice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13772C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13772C\"></sup>to the rumbling that comes from his mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13772D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13772D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He unleashes his lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13773E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13773E\"></sup> beneath the whole heavenand sends it to the ends of the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13773F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13773F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>After that comes the sound of his roar;he thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13774G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13774G\"></sup> with his majestic voice.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13774H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13774H\"></sup>When his voice resounds,he holds nothing back.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>God’s voice thunders<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13775I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13775I\"></sup> in marvelous ways;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13775J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13775J\"></sup>he does great things beyond our understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13775K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13775K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He says to the snow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13776L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13776L\"></sup> ‘Fall on the earth,’and to the rain shower, ‘Be a mighty downpour.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13776M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13776M\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So that everyone he has made may know his work,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13777N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13777N\"></sup>he stops all people from their labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13777O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13777O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The animals take cover;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13778P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13778P\"></sup>they remain in their dens.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13778Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13778Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The tempest comes out from its chamber,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13779R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13779R\"></sup>the cold from the driving winds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13779S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13779S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The breath of God produces ice,and the broad waters become frozen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13780T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13780T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He loads the clouds with moisture;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13781U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13781U\"></sup>he scatters his lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13781V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13781V\"></sup> through them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13781W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13781W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>At his direction they swirl aroundover the face of the whole earthto do whatever he commands them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13782X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13782X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He brings the clouds to punish people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13783Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13783Y\"></sup>or to water his earth and show his love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13783Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13783Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Listen<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13784AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13784AA\"></sup> to this, Job;stop and consider God’s wonders.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13784AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13784AB\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do you know how God controls the cloudsand makes his lightning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13785AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13785AC\"></sup> flash?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13785AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13785AD\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do you know how the clouds hang poised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13786AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13786AE\"></sup>those wonders of him who has perfect knowledge?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13786AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13786AF\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You who swelter in your clotheswhen the land lies hushed under the south wind,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13787AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13787AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>can you join him in spreading out the skies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13788AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13788AH\"></sup>hard as a mirror of cast bronze?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13788AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13788AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Tell us what we should say to him;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13789AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13789AJ\"></sup>we cannot draw up our case<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13789AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13789AK\"></sup> because of our darkness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13789AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13789AL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Should he be told that I want to speak?Would anyone ask to be swallowed up?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now no one can look at the sun,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13791AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13791AM\"></sup>bright as it is in the skiesafter the wind has swept them clean.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Out of the north he comes in golden splendor;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13792AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13792AN\"></sup>God comes in awesome majesty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13792AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13792AO\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The Almighty is beyond our reach and exalted in power;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13793AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13793AP\"></sup>in his justice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13793AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13793AQ\"></sup> and great righteousness, he does not oppress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13793AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13793AR\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore, people revere him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13794AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13794AS\"></sup>for does he not have regard for all the wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13794AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13794AT\"></sup> in heart?”"
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Job<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13795A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13795A\"></sup> out of the storm.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13795B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13795B\"></sup> He said:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Who is this that obscures my plans<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13796C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13796C\"></sup>with words without knowledge?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13796D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13796D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Brace yourself like a man;I will question you,and you shall answer me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13797E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13797E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Where were you when I laid the earth’s foundation?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13798F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13798F\"></sup>Tell me, if you understand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13798G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13798G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who marked off its dimensions?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13799H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13799H\"></sup> Surely you know!Who stretched a measuring line<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13799I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13799I\"></sup> across it?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On what were its footings set,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13800J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13800J\"></sup>or who laid its cornerstone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13800K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13800K\"></sup>—",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>while the morning stars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13801L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13801L\"></sup> sang together<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13801M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13801M\"></sup>and all the angels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13801N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13801N\"></sup> shouted for joy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13801O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13801O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Who shut up the sea behind doors<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13802P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13802P\"></sup>when it burst forth from the womb,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13802Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13802Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>when I made the clouds its garmentand wrapped it in thick darkness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13803R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13803R\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>when I fixed limits for it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13804S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13804S\"></sup>and set its doors and bars in place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13804T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13804T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>when I said, ‘This far you may come and no farther;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13805U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13805U\"></sup>here is where your proud waves halt’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13805V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13805V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Have you ever given orders to the morning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13806W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13806W\"></sup>or shown the dawn its place,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13806X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13806X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>that it might take the earth by the edgesand shake the wicked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13807Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13807Y\"></sup> out of it?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13807Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13807Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The earth takes shape like clay under a seal;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13808AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13808AA\"></sup>its features stand out like those of a garment.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The wicked are denied their light,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13809AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13809AB\"></sup>and their upraised arm is broken.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13809AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13809AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Have you journeyed to the springs of the seaor walked in the recesses of the deep?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13810AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13810AD\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Have the gates of death<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13811AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13811AE\"></sup> been shown to you?Have you seen the gates of the deepest darkness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13811AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13811AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Have you comprehended the vast expanses of the earth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13812AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13812AG\"></sup>Tell me, if you know all this.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13812AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13812AH\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“What is the way to the abode of light?And where does darkness reside?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13813AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13813AI\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Can you take them to their places?Do you know the paths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13814AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13814AJ\"></sup> to their dwellings?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Surely you know, for you were already born!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13815AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13815AK\"></sup>You have lived so many years!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Have you entered the storehouses of the snow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13816AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13816AL\"></sup>or seen the storehouses<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13816AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13816AM\"></sup> of the hail,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13816AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13816AN\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>which I reserve for times of trouble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13817AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13817AO\"></sup>for days of war and battle?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13817AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13817AP\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>What is the way to the place where the lightning is dispersed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13818AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13818AQ\"></sup>or the place where the east winds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13818AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13818AR\"></sup> are scattered over the earth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13818AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13818AS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Who cuts a channel for the torrents of rain,and a path for the thunderstorm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13819AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13819AT\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>to water<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13820AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13820AU\"></sup> a land where no one lives,an uninhabited desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13820AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13820AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>to satisfy a desolate wastelandand make it sprout with grass?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13821AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13821AW\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Does the rain have a father?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13822AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13822AX\"></sup>Who fathers the drops of dew?",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>From whose womb comes the ice?Who gives birth to the frost from the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13823AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13823AY\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>when the waters become hard as stone,when the surface of the deep is frozen?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13824AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13824AZ\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Can you bind the chains of the Pleiades?Can you loosen Orion’s belt?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13825BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13825BA\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Can you bring forth the constellations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13826BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13826BB\"></sup> in their seasonsor lead out the Bear with its cubs?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13826BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13826BC\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Do you know the laws<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13827BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13827BD\"></sup> of the heavens?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13827BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13827BE\"></sup>Can you set up God’s dominion over the earth?",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Can you raise your voice to the cloudsand cover yourself with a flood of water?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13828BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13828BF\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Do you send the lightning bolts on their way?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13829BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13829BG\"></sup>Do they report to you, ‘Here we are’?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Who gives the ibis wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13830BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13830BH\"></sup>or gives the rooster understanding?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13830BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13830BI\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Who has the wisdom to count the clouds?Who can tip over the water jars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13831BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13831BJ\"></sup> of the heavens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13831BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13831BK\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>when the dust becomes hard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13832BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13832BL\"></sup>and the clods of earth stick together?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13832BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13832BM\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>“Do you hunt the prey for the lionessand satisfy the hunger of the lions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13833BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13833BN\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>when they crouch in their dens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13834BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13834BO\"></sup>or lie in wait in a thicket?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13834BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13834BP\"></sup>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Who provides food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13835BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13835BQ\"></sup> for the raven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13835BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13835BR\"></sup>when its young cry out to Godand wander about for lack of food?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13835BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13835BS\"></sup>"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span>“Do you know when the mountain goats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13836A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13836A\"></sup> give birth?Do you watch when the doe bears her fawn?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13836B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13836B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Do you count the months till they bear?Do you know the time they give birth?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13837C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13837C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They crouch down and bring forth their young;their labor pains are ended.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Their young thrive and grow strong in the wilds;they leave and do not return.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Who let the wild donkey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13840D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13840D\"></sup> go free?Who untied its ropes?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I gave it the wasteland<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13841E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13841E\"></sup> as its home,the salt flats<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13841F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13841F\"></sup> as its habitat.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13841G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13841G\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It laughs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13842H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13842H\"></sup> at the commotion in the town;it does not hear a driver’s shout.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13842I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13842I\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It ranges the hills<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13843J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13843J\"></sup> for its pastureand searches for any green thing.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Will the wild ox<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13844K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13844K\"></sup> consent to serve you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13844L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13844L\"></sup>Will it stay by your manger<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13844M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13844M\"></sup> at night?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Can you hold it to the furrow with a harness?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13845N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13845N\"></sup>Will it till the valleys behind you?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Will you rely on it for its great strength?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13846O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13846O\"></sup>Will you leave your heavy work to it?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Can you trust it to haul in your grainand bring it to your threshing floor?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The wings of the ostrich flap joyfully,though they cannot comparewith the wings and feathers of the stork.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13848P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13848P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>She lays her eggs on the groundand lets them warm in the sand,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>unmindful that a foot may crush them,that some wild animal may trample them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13850Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13850Q\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>She treats her young harshly,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13851R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13851R\"></sup> as if they were not hers;she cares not that her labor was in vain,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for God did not endow her with wisdomor give her a share of good sense.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13852S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13852S\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Yet when she spreads her feathers to run,she laughs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13853T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13853T\"></sup> at horse and rider.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Do you give the horse its strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13854U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13854U\"></sup>or clothe its neck with a flowing mane?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Do you make it leap like a locust,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13855V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13855V\"></sup>striking terror<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13855W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13855W\"></sup> with its proud snorting?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13855X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13855X\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>It paws fiercely, rejoicing in its strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13856Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13856Y\"></sup>and charges into the fray.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13856Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13856Z\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It laughs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13857AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13857AA\"></sup> at fear, afraid of nothing;it does not shy away from the sword.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The quiver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13858AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13858AB\"></sup> rattles against its side,along with the flashing spear<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13858AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13858AC\"></sup> and lance.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In frenzied excitement it eats up the ground;it cannot stand still when the trumpet sounds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13859AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13859AD\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>At the blast of the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13860AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13860AE\"></sup> it snorts, ‘Aha!’It catches the scent of battle from afar,the shout of commanders and the battle cry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13860AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13860AF\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Does the hawk take flight by your wisdomand spread its wings toward the south?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13861AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13861AG\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Does the eagle soar at your commandand build its nest on high?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13862AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13862AH\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>It dwells on a cliff and stays there at night;a rocky crag<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13863AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13863AI\"></sup> is its stronghold.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>From there it looks for food;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13864AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13864AJ\"></sup>its eyes detect it from afar.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Its young ones feast on blood,and where the slain are, there it is.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13865AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13865AK\"></sup>"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Job:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13866A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13866A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Will the one who contends with the Almighty<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13867B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13867B\"></sup> correct him?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13867C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13867C\"></sup>Let him who accuses God answer him!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13867D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13867D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Job answered the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I am unworthy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13869E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13869E\"></sup>—how can I reply to you?I put my hand over my mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13869F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13869F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I spoke once, but I have no answer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13870G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13870G\"></sup>—twice, but I will say no more.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13870H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13870H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to Job out of the storm:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13871I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13871I\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Brace yourself like a man;I will question you,and you shall answer me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13872J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13872J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Would you discredit my justice?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13873K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13873K\"></sup>Would you condemn me to justify yourself?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13873L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13873L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do you have an arm like God’s,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13874M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13874M\"></sup>and can your voice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13874N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13874N\"></sup> thunder like his?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13874O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13874O\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then adorn yourself with glory and splendor,and clothe yourself in honor and majesty.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13875P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13875P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Unleash the fury of your wrath,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13876Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13876Q\"></sup>look at all who are proud and bring them low,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13876R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13876R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>look at all who are proud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13877S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13877S\"></sup> and humble them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13877T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13877T\"></sup>crush<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13877U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13877U\"></sup> the wicked where they stand.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Bury them all in the dust together;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13878V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13878V\"></sup>shroud their faces in the grave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13878W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13878W\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I myself will admit to youthat your own right hand can save you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13879X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13879X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Look at Behemoth,which I made<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13880Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13880Y\"></sup> along with youand which feeds on grass like an ox.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13880Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13880Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>What strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13881AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13881AA\"></sup> it has in its loins,what power in the muscles of its belly!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13881AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13881AB\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Its tail sways like a cedar;the sinews of its thighs are close-knit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13882AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13882AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Its bones are tubes of bronze,its limbs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13883AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13883AD\"></sup> like rods of iron.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13883AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13883AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>It ranks first among the works of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13884AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13884AF\"></sup>yet its Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13884AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13884AG\"></sup> can approach it with his sword.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13884AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13884AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The hills bring it their produce,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13885AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13885AI\"></sup>and all the wild animals play<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13885AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13885AJ\"></sup> nearby.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13885AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13885AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Under the lotus plants it lies,hidden among the reeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13886AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13886AL\"></sup> in the marsh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13886AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13886AM\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The lotuses conceal it in their shadow;the poplars by the stream<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13887AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13887AN\"></sup> surround it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>A raging river<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13888AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13888AO\"></sup> does not alarm it;it is secure, though the Jordan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13888AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13888AP\"></sup> should surge against its mouth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Can anyone capture it by the eyes,or trap it and pierce its nose?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13889AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13889AQ\"></sup>"
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>“Can you pull in Leviathan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13890A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13890A\"></sup> with a fishhook<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13890B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13890B\"></sup>or tie down its tongue with a rope?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Can you put a cord through its nose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13891C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13891C\"></sup>or pierce its jaw with a hook?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13891D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13891D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Will it keep begging you for mercy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13892E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13892E\"></sup>Will it speak to you with gentle words?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Will it make an agreement with youfor you to take it as your slave for life?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13893F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13893F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Can you make a pet of it like a birdor put it on a leash for the young women in your house?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Will traders barter for it?Will they divide it up among the merchants?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Can you fill its hide with harpoonsor its head with fishing spears?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13896G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13896G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If you lay a hand on it,you will remember the struggle and never do it again!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13897H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13897H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Any hope of subduing it is false;the mere sight of it is overpowering.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13898I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13898I\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>No one is fierce enough to rouse it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13899J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13899J\"></sup>Who then is able to stand against me?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13899K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13899K\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Who has a claim against me that I must pay?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13900L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13900L\"></sup>Everything under heaven belongs to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13900M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13900M\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will not fail to speak of Leviathan’s limbs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13901N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13901N\"></sup>its strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13901O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13901O\"></sup> and its graceful form.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who can strip off its outer coat?Who can penetrate its double coat of armor?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13902P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13902P\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Who dares open the doors of its mouth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13903Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13903Q\"></sup>ringed about with fearsome teeth?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Its back has rows of shieldstightly sealed together;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13904R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13904R\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>each is so close to the nextthat no air can pass between.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They are joined fast to one another;they cling together and cannot be parted.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Its snorting throws out flashes of light;its eyes are like the rays of dawn.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13907S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13907S\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Flames<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13908T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13908T\"></sup> stream from its mouth;sparks of fire shoot out.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Smoke pours from its nostrils<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13909U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13909U\"></sup>as from a boiling pot over burning reeds.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Its breath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13910V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13910V\"></sup> sets coals ablaze,and flames dart from its mouth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13910W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13910W\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Strength<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13911X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13911X\"></sup> resides in its neck;dismay goes before it.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The folds of its flesh are tightly joined;they are firm and immovable.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Its chest is hard as rock,hard as a lower millstone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13913Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13913Y\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When it rises up, the mighty are terrified;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13914Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13914Z\"></sup>they retreat before its thrashing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13914AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13914AA\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The sword that reaches it has no effect,nor does the spear or the dart or the javelin.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13915AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13915AB\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Iron it treats like straw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13916AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13916AC\"></sup>and bronze like rotten wood.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Arrows do not make it flee;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13917AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13917AD\"></sup>slingstones are like chaff to it.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A club seems to it but a piece of straw;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13918AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13918AE\"></sup>it laughs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13918AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13918AF\"></sup> at the rattling of the lance.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Its undersides are jagged potsherds,leaving a trail in the mud like a threshing sledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13919AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13919AG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>It makes the depths churn like a boiling caldron<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13920AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13920AH\"></sup>and stirs up the sea like a pot of ointment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13920AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13920AI\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>It leaves a glistening wake behind it;one would think the deep had white hair.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Nothing on earth is its equal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13922AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13922AJ\"></sup>—a creature without fear.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>It looks down on all that are haughty;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13923AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13923AK\"></sup>it is king over all that are proud.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13923AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13923AL\"></sup>”"
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>Then Job replied to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I know that you can do all things;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13925A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13925A\"></sup>no purpose of yours can be thwarted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13925B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13925B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You asked, ‘Who is this that obscures my plans without knowledge?’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13926C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13926C\"></sup>Surely I spoke of things I did not understand,things too wonderful for me to know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13926D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13926D\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“You said, ‘Listen now, and I will speak;I will question you,and you shall answer me.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13927E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13927E\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My ears had heard of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13928F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13928F\"></sup>but now my eyes have seen you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13928G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13928G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore I despise myself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13929H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13929H\"></sup>and repent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13929I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13929I\"></sup> in dust and ashes.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13929J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13929J\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had said these things to Job<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13930K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13930K\"></sup>, he said to Eliphaz the Temanite, “I am angry with you and your two friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13930L\"></sup> because you have not spoken the truth about me, as my servant Job has.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13930M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13930M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So now take seven bulls and seven rams<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931N\"></sup> and go to my servant Job<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931O\"></sup> and sacrifice a burnt offering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931P\"></sup> for yourselves. My servant Job will pray for you, and I will accept his prayer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931Q\"></sup> and not deal with you according to your folly.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931R\"></sup> You have not spoken the truth about me, as my servant Job has.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13931S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13931S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So Eliphaz the Temanite, Bildad the Shuhite and Zophar the Naamathite<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13932T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13932T\"></sup> did what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> told them; and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> accepted Job’s prayer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13932U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13932U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>After Job had prayed for his friends, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> restored his fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13933V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13933V\"></sup> and gave him twice as much as he had before.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13933W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13933W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All his brothers and sisters and everyone who had known him before<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13934X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13934X\"></sup> came and ate with him in his house. They comforted and consoled him over all the trouble the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> had brought on him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13934Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13934Y\"></sup> and each one gave him a piece of silver and a gold ring.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blessed the latter part of Job’s life more than the former part. He had fourteen thousand sheep, six thousand camels, a thousand yoke of oxen and a thousand donkeys.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he also had seven sons and three daughters.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The first daughter he named Jemimah, the second Keziah and the third Keren-Happuch.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Nowhere in all the land were there found women as beautiful as Job’s daughters, and their father granted them an inheritance along with their brothers.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>After this, Job lived a hundred and forty years; he saw his children and their children to the fourth generation.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And so Job died, an old man and full of years.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-13940Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-13940Z\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;